32CAdjEulerSolver::CAdjEulerSolver() : CSolver() {
33
34 /*--- Array initialization ---*/
35 Phi_Inf = nullptr;
36 Sens_Mach = nullptr;
37 Sens_AoA = nullptr;
38 Sens_Geo = nullptr;
39 Sens_Press = nullptr;
40 Sens_Temp = nullptr;
41 Sens_BPress = nullptr;
42 Jacobian_Axisymmetric = nullptr;
43 CSensitivity = nullptr;
44 FlowPrimVar_i = nullptr;
45 FlowPrimVar_j = nullptr;
46

49CAdjEulerSolver::CAdjEulerSolver(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) : CSolver() {
50 unsigned long iPoint, iVertex, iMarker, jMarker;
51 string text_line, mesh_filename;
52 unsigned short iDim, iVar;
53 ifstream restart_file;
54 string filename, AdjExt;
55 su2double myArea_Monitored, *Normal;
56
57 adjoint = true;
58
59 bool restart = config->GetRestart();
60
61 bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
62
63 su2double RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
64 su2double RefDensity = config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
65 su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
66 su2double Mach_Motion = config->GetMach_Motion();
67 su2double RefVel2, Mach2Vel, Weight_ObjFunc, factor;
68 su2double *Velocity_Inf;
69 string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
70 unsigned short iMarker_Monitoring, ObjFunc;
71 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
72
73 /*--- Array initialization ---*/
74
75 Phi_Inf = nullptr;
76 Sens_Mach = nullptr;
77 Sens_AoA = nullptr;
78 Sens_Geo = nullptr;
79 Sens_Press = nullptr;
80 Sens_Temp = nullptr;
81 Sens_BPress = nullptr;
82 Jacobian_Axisymmetric = nullptr;
83 CSensitivity = nullptr;
84 FlowPrimVar_i = nullptr;
85 FlowPrimVar_j = nullptr;
86
87 /*--- Set the gamma value ---*/
88 Gamma = config->GetGamma();
89 Gamma_Minus_One = Gamma - 1.0;
90
91 /*--- Define geometry constans in the solver structure ---*/
92 nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
93 nMarker = config->GetnMarker_All();
94 nPoint = geometry->GetnPoint();
95 nPointDomain = geometry->GetnPointDomain();
96
97 nVar = nDim + 2;
98
99 /*--- Initialize nVarGrad for deallocation ---*/
100
101 nVarGrad = nVar;
102
103 Residual_RMS.resize(nVar,0.0);
104 Residual_Max.resize(nVar,0.0);
105 Point_Max.resize(nVar,0);
106 Point_Max_Coord.resize(nVar,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
107
108 /*--- Define some auxiliary vectors related to the residual ---*/
109 Residual = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Residual[iVar] = 0.0;
110 Residual_i = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Residual_i[iVar] = 0.0;
111 Residual_j = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Residual_j[iVar] = 0.0;
112 Res_Conv_i = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Res_Conv_i[iVar] = 0.0;
113 Res_Visc_i = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Res_Visc_i[iVar] = 0.0;
114 Res_Conv_j = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Res_Conv_j[iVar] = 0.0;
115 Res_Visc_j = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Res_Visc_j[iVar] = 0.0;
116
117 /*--- Define some auxiliary vectors related to the solution ---*/
118 Solution = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Solution[iVar] = 0.0;
119 Solution_i = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Solution_i[iVar] = 0.0;
120 Solution_j = new su2double[nVar]; for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Solution_j[iVar] = 0.0;
121
122 /*--- Define some auxiliary arrays related to the flow solution ---*/
123 FlowPrimVar_i = new su2double[nDim+7]();
124 FlowPrimVar_j = new su2double[nDim+7]();
125
126 /*--- Define some auxiliary vectors related to the geometry ---*/
127 Vector = new su2double[nDim]; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Vector[iDim] = 0.0;
128 Vector_i = new su2double[nDim]; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Vector_i[iDim] = 0.0;
129 Vector_j = new su2double[nDim]; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Vector_j[iDim] = 0.0;
130
131 /*--- Define some auxiliary vectors related to the undivided lapalacian ---*/
132 if (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_AdjFlow() == SPACE_CENTERED) {
133 iPoint_UndLapl.resize(nPoint);
134 jPoint_UndLapl.resize(nPoint);
135 }
136
137 /*--- Point to point Jacobians. These are always defined because
138 they are also used for sensitivity calculations. ---*/
139 Jacobian_i = new su2double* [nVar];
140 Jacobian_j = new su2double* [nVar];
141 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
142 Jacobian_i[iVar] = new su2double [nVar];
143 Jacobian_j[iVar] = new su2double [nVar];
144 }
145
146 LinSysSol.Initialize(nPoint, nPointDomain, nVar, 0.0);
147 LinSysRes.Initialize(nPoint, nPointDomain, nVar, 0.0);
148
149 /*--- Jacobians and vector structures for implicit computations ---*/
150 if (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_AdjFlow() == EULER_IMPLICIT) {
151 Jacobian_ii = new su2double* [nVar];
152 Jacobian_ij = new su2double* [nVar];
153 Jacobian_ji = new su2double* [nVar];
154 Jacobian_jj = new su2double* [nVar];
155 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
156 Jacobian_ii[iVar] = new su2double [nVar];
157 Jacobian_ij[iVar] = new su2double [nVar];
158 Jacobian_ji[iVar] = new su2double [nVar];
159 Jacobian_jj[iVar] = new su2double [nVar];
160 }
161
162 if (rank == MASTER_NODE)
163 cout << "Initialize Jacobian structure (Adjoint Euler). MG level: " << iMesh <<"." << endl;
164 Jacobian.Initialize(nPoint, nPointDomain, nVar, nVar, true, geometry, config);
165
166 if (axisymmetric) {
167 Jacobian_Axisymmetric = new su2double* [nVar];
168 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
169 Jacobian_Axisymmetric[iVar] = new su2double [nVar];
170 }
171 } else {
172 if (rank == MASTER_NODE)
173 cout << "Explicit scheme. No Jacobian structure (Adjoint Euler). MG level: " << iMesh <<"." << endl;
174 }
175
176 /*--- Sensitivity definition and coefficient in all the markers ---*/
177 CSensitivity = new su2double* [nMarker];
178 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
179 CSensitivity[iMarker] = new su2double [geometry->nVertex[iMarker]];
180 }
181
182 /*--- Store the value of the characteristic primitive variables at the boundaries ---*/
183
184 DonorAdjVar.resize(nMarker);
185 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
186 DonorAdjVar[iMarker].resize(geometry->nVertex[iMarker]);
187 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
188 DonorAdjVar[iMarker][iVertex].resize(nVar, 0.0);
189 }
190 }
191
192 /*--- Store the value of the characteristic primitive variables index at the boundaries ---*/
193
194 DonorGlobalIndex.resize(nMarker);
195 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
196 DonorGlobalIndex[iMarker].resize(geometry->nVertex[iMarker],0);
197 }
198
199 Sens_Geo = new su2double[nMarker];
200 Sens_Mach = new su2double[nMarker];
201 Sens_AoA = new su2double[nMarker];
202 Sens_Press = new su2double[nMarker];
203 Sens_Temp = new su2double[nMarker];
204 Sens_BPress = new su2double[nMarker];
205
206 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
207 Sens_Geo[iMarker] = 0.0;
208 Sens_Mach[iMarker] = 0.0;
209 Sens_AoA[iMarker] = 0.0;
210 Sens_Press[iMarker] = 0.0;
211 Sens_Temp[iMarker] = 0.0;
212 Sens_BPress[iMarker] = 0.0;
213 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++)
214 CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex] = 0.0;
215 }
216
217 /*--- Adjoint flow at the inifinity, initialization stuff ---*/
218 PsiRho_Inf = 0.0; PsiE_Inf = 0.0;
219 Phi_Inf = new su2double [nDim];
220 Phi_Inf[0] = 0.0; Phi_Inf[1] = 0.0;
221 if (nDim == 3) Phi_Inf[2] = 0.0;
222
223 /*--- If outflow objective, nonzero initialization ---*/
224 if ((config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE)) {
225 su2double SoundSpeed,*vel_inf,R,vel2,vel;
226 R = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
227 vel_inf = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND();
228 vel2=0;
229 for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++)
230 vel2 +=vel_inf[iDim]*vel_inf[iDim];
231 vel = pow(vel2,0.5);
232 SoundSpeed= pow(Gamma*config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND()*R, 0.5);
233 PsiE_Inf = Gamma_Minus_One*vel2/(vel2-pow(SoundSpeed,2.0))*0.5/vel;
234 PsiRho_Inf += PsiE_Inf*(2*SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed+vel2*Gamma_Minus_One)/(2.0*Gamma_Minus_One);
235 // Assumes +x flow direction
236 // Assume v.n = |v|, n = -v/|v|
237
238 for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++) {
239 Phi_Inf[iDim] +=PsiE_Inf*(SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One/vel2-1)*vel_inf[iDim];
240 // Assumes n in direction of v
241 Phi_Inf[iDim]+=vel_inf[iDim]/vel*(0.5);
242 }
243
244 }
245
246 /*--- Initialize the solution with the far-field state everywhere. ---*/
247
248 nodes = new CAdjEulerVariable(PsiRho_Inf, Phi_Inf, PsiE_Inf, nPoint, nDim, nVar, config);
249 SetBaseClassPointerToNodes();
250
251 /*--- Read the restart metadata. ---*/
252
253 if (restart && (iMesh == MESH_0)) {
254 mesh_filename = config->GetSolution_AdjFileName();
255 filename = config->GetObjFunc_Extension(mesh_filename);
256// Read_SU2_Restart_Metadata(geometry, config, true, filename);
257 }
258
259 /*--- Define solver parameters needed for execution of destructor ---*/
260
261 space_centered = config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_AdjFlow() == SPACE_CENTERED;
262
263
264 /*--- Calculate area monitored for area-averaged-outflow-quantity-based objectives ---*/
265
266 myArea_Monitored = 0.0;
267 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
268 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring)==SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE ||
269 config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring)==SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE) {
270
271 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
272 /*-- Find the marker index ---*/
273 iMarker = 0;
274 for (jMarker= 0; jMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); jMarker++) {
275 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(jMarker);
276 if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) {
277 iMarker = jMarker;
278 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
279 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
280 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
281 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
282 myArea_Monitored += GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
283 }
284 }
285 break;
286 }
287 }
288 }
289 }
290
291#ifdef HAVE_MPI
292 Area_Monitored = 0.0;
293 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&myArea_Monitored, &Area_Monitored, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
294#else
295 Area_Monitored = myArea_Monitored;
296#endif
297
298 if (config->GetnObj() > 1 && iMesh==MESH_0) {
299 if (grid_movement) {
300 Mach2Vel = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND());
301 RefVel2 = (Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel)*(Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel);
302 }
303 else {
304 Velocity_Inf = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND();
305 RefVel2 = 0.0;
306 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
307 RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
308 }
309
310 /*--- Objective scaling: a factor must be applied to certain objectives ---*/
311 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
312 Weight_ObjFunc = config->GetWeight_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
313
314 factor = 1.0/(0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);
315
316 ObjFunc = config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
317 if ((ObjFunc == INVERSE_DESIGN_HEATFLUX) ||
318 (ObjFunc == TOTAL_HEATFLUX) || (ObjFunc == MAXIMUM_HEATFLUX) ||
319 (ObjFunc == SURFACE_MASSFLOW) ) factor = 1.0;
320
321 if ((ObjFunc == SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE) || (ObjFunc == SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE))
322 factor = 1.0/Area_Monitored;
323
324 Weight_ObjFunc = Weight_ObjFunc*factor;
325 config->SetWeight_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring, Weight_ObjFunc);
326 }
327 }
328
329 /*--- MPI solution ---*/
330
331 InitiateComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
332 CompleteComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
333
334 SolverName = "ADJ.FLOW";
335}

337CAdjEulerSolver::~CAdjEulerSolver() {
338 unsigned short iVar, iMarker;
339
340 delete [] Phi_Inf;
341 delete [] Sens_Mach;
342 delete [] Sens_AoA;
343 delete [] Sens_Geo;
344 delete [] Sens_Press;
345 delete [] Sens_Temp;
346 delete [] Sens_BPress;
347 delete [] FlowPrimVar_i;
348 delete [] FlowPrimVar_j;
349
350 if (Jacobian_Axisymmetric != nullptr) {
351 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
352 delete Jacobian_Axisymmetric[iVar];
353 delete [] Jacobian_Axisymmetric;
354 }
355
356 if (CSensitivity != nullptr) {
357 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++)
358 delete [] CSensitivity[iMarker];
359 delete [] CSensitivity;
360 }
361
362 delete nodes;
363}

365void CAdjEulerSolver::SetTime_Step(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config,
366 unsigned short iMesh, unsigned long Iteration) {
367
368 /*--- Use the flow solution to update the time step
369 * The time step depends on the characteristic velocity, which is the same
370 * for the adjoint and flow solutions, albeit in the opposite direction. ---*/
371 solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->SetTime_Step(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Iteration);
372}

374void CAdjEulerSolver::Set_MPI_ActDisk(CSolver **solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
375
376 unsigned long iter, iPoint, iVertex, jVertex, iPointTotal,
377 Buffer_Send_nPointTotal = 0, iGlobalIndex, iGlobal;
378 unsigned short iVar, iMarker, jMarker;
379 long nDomain = 0, iDomain, jDomain;
380
381 /*--- MPI status and request arrays for non-blocking communications ---*/
382
383 SU2_MPI::Status status;
384 SU2_MPI::Request req;
385
386 /*--- Define buffer vector interior domain ---*/
387
388 su2double *Buffer_Send_AdjVar = nullptr;
389 auto *iAdjVar = new su2double [nVar];
390
391 auto *nPointTotal_s = new unsigned long[size];
392 auto *nPointTotal_r = new unsigned long[size];
393
394 unsigned long Buffer_Size_AdjVar = 0;
395 unsigned long PointTotal_Counter = 0;
396
397 /*--- Allocate the memory that we only need if we have MPI support ---*/
398
399 su2double *Buffer_Receive_AdjVar = nullptr;
400
401 /*--- Basic dimensionalization ---*/
402
403 nDomain = size;
404
405 /*--- This loop gets the array sizes of points for each
406 rank to send to each other rank. ---*/
407
408 for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
409
410 /*--- Loop over the markers to perform the dimensionalizaton
411 of the domain variables ---*/
412
413 Buffer_Send_nPointTotal = 0;
414
415 /*--- Loop over all of the markers and count the number of each
416 type of point and element that needs to be sent. ---*/
417
418 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
419 if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
420 (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
421 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
422 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
423 jDomain = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorProcessor();
424 if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))) {
425 Buffer_Send_nPointTotal++;
426 }
427 }
428 }
429 }
430
431 /*--- Store the counts on a partition by partition basis. ---*/
432
433 nPointTotal_s[iDomain] = Buffer_Send_nPointTotal;
434
435 /*--- Total counts for allocating send buffers below ---*/
436
437 Buffer_Size_AdjVar += nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nVar+3);
438
439 }
440
441 /*--- Allocate the buffer vectors in the appropiate domain (master, iDomain) ---*/
442
443 Buffer_Send_AdjVar = new su2double[Buffer_Size_AdjVar];
444
445 /*--- Now that we know the sizes of the point, we can
446 allocate and send the information in large chunks to all processors. ---*/
447
448 for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
449
450 /*--- A rank does not communicate with itself through MPI ---*/
451
452 if (rank != iDomain) {
453
454 /*--- Communicate the counts to iDomain with non-blocking sends ---*/
455
456 SU2_MPI::Isend(&nPointTotal_s[iDomain], 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, iDomain, iDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
457 SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
458
459 } else {
460
461 /*--- If iDomain = rank, we simply copy values into place in memory ---*/
462
463 nPointTotal_r[iDomain] = nPointTotal_s[iDomain];
464
465 }
466
467 /*--- Receive the counts. All processors are sending their counters to
468 iDomain up above, so only iDomain needs to perform the recv here from
469 all other ranks. ---*/
470
471 if (rank == iDomain) {
472
473 for (jDomain = 0; jDomain < size; jDomain++) {
474
475 /*--- A rank does not communicate with itself through MPI ---*/
476
477 if (rank != jDomain) {
478
479 /*--- Recv the data by probing for the current sender, jDomain,
480 first and then receiving the values from it. ---*/
481
482 SU2_MPI::Recv(&nPointTotal_r[jDomain], 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, jDomain, rank, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
483
484 }
485 }
486
487 }
488 }
489
490 /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
491
492 SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
493
494 /*--- Initialize the counters for the larger send buffers (by domain) ---*/
495
496 PointTotal_Counter = 0;
497
498 for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
499
500 /*--- Set the value of the interior geometry. Initialize counters. ---*/
501
502 iPointTotal = 0;
503
504 /*--- Load up the actual values into the buffers for sending. ---*/
505
506 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
507
508 if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
509 (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
510
511 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
512 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
513 jDomain = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorProcessor();
514 if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))) {
515
516 iGlobalIndex = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint);
517 jVertex = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorVertex();
518 jMarker = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorMarker();
519
520 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
521 Buffer_Send_AdjVar[(nVar+3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+iVar] = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iVar);
522 }
523 Buffer_Send_AdjVar[(nVar+3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(nVar+0)] = su2double(iGlobalIndex);
524 Buffer_Send_AdjVar[(nVar+3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(nVar+1)] = su2double(jVertex);
525 Buffer_Send_AdjVar[(nVar+3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(nVar+2)] = su2double(jMarker);
526
527 iPointTotal++;
528
529 }
530
531 }
532
533 }
534
535 }
536
537 /*--- Send the buffers with the geometrical information ---*/
538
539 if (iDomain != rank) {
540
541 /*--- Communicate the coordinates, global index, colors, and element
542 date to iDomain with non-blocking sends. ---*/
543
544 SU2_MPI::Isend(&Buffer_Send_AdjVar[PointTotal_Counter*(nVar+3)],
545 nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nVar+3), MPI_DOUBLE, iDomain,
546 iDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
547 SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
548 }
549
550 else {
551
552 /*--- Allocate local memory for the local recv of the elements ---*/
553
554 Buffer_Receive_AdjVar = new su2double[nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nVar+3)];
555
556 for (iter = 0; iter < nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nVar+3); iter++)
557 Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iter] = Buffer_Send_AdjVar[PointTotal_Counter*(nVar+3)+iter];
558
559 /*--- Recv the point data from ourselves (same procedure as above) ---*/
560
561 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointTotal_r[iDomain]; iPoint++) {
562
563 iGlobal = SU2_TYPE::Int(Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+(nVar+0)]);
564 iVertex = SU2_TYPE::Int(Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+(nVar+1)]);
565 iMarker = SU2_TYPE::Int(Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+(nVar+2)]);
566 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
567 iAdjVar[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+iVar];
568
569 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
570 SetDonorAdjVar(iMarker, iVertex, iVar, iAdjVar[iVar]);
571
572 SetDonorGlobalIndex(iMarker, iVertex, iGlobal);
573
574 }
575
576 /*--- Delete memory for recv the point stuff ---*/
577
578 delete [] Buffer_Receive_AdjVar;
579
580 }
581
582 /*--- Increment the counters for the send buffers (iDomain loop) ---*/
583
584 PointTotal_Counter += iPointTotal;
585
586 }
587
588 /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
589
590 SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
591
592 /*--- The next section begins the recv of all data for the interior
593 points/elements in the mesh. First, create the domain structures for
594 the points on this rank. First, we recv all of the point data ---*/
595
596 for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < size; iDomain++) {
597
598 if (rank != iDomain) {
599
600#ifdef HAVE_MPI
601
602 /*--- Allocate the receive buffer vector. Send the colors so that we
603 know whether what we recv is an owned or halo node. ---*/
604
605 Buffer_Receive_AdjVar = new su2double [nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*nVar];
606
607 /*--- Receive the buffers with the coords, global index, and colors ---*/
608
609 SU2_MPI::Recv(Buffer_Receive_AdjVar, nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(nVar+3) , MPI_DOUBLE,
610 iDomain, rank, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
611
612 /*--- Loop over all of the points that we have recv'd and store the
613 coords, global index vertex and markers ---*/
614
615 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointTotal_r[iDomain]; iPoint++) {
616
617 iGlobal = SU2_TYPE::Int(Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+(nVar+0)]);
618 iVertex = SU2_TYPE::Int(Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+(nVar+1)]);
619 iMarker = SU2_TYPE::Int(Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+(nVar+2)]);
620 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
621 iAdjVar[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_AdjVar[iPoint*(nVar+3)+iVar];
622
623 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
624 SetDonorAdjVar(iMarker, iVertex, iVar, iAdjVar[iVar]);
625
626 SetDonorGlobalIndex(iMarker, iVertex, iGlobal);
627
628 }
629
630 /*--- Delete memory for recv the point stuff ---*/
631
632 delete [] Buffer_Receive_AdjVar;
633
634#endif
635
636 }
637
638 }
639
640 /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
641
642 SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
643
644 /*--- Free all of the memory used for communicating points and elements ---*/
645
646 delete[] Buffer_Send_AdjVar;
647
648 /*--- Release all of the temporary memory ---*/
649
650 delete [] nPointTotal_s;
651 delete [] nPointTotal_r;
652 delete [] iAdjVar;
653
654}
655
656void CAdjEulerSolver::SetForceProj_Vector(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config) {
657
658 su2double *ForceProj_Vector, x = 0.0, y = 0.0, z = 0.0, *Normal, CD, CL, Cp, CpTarget,
659 CT, CQ, x_origin, y_origin, z_origin, WDrag, Area, invCD, CLCD2, invCQ, CTRCQ2;
660 unsigned short iMarker,jMarker,iMarker_Monitoring, iDim;
661 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
662 string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
663 su2double Weight_ObjFunc=1.0;
664 su2double *ForceProj_Vector2;
665
666 su2double Alpha = (config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER)/180.0;
667 su2double Beta = (config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER)/180.0;
668 su2double RefLength = config->GetRefLength();
669 const auto RefOriginMoment = config->GetRefOriginMoment(0);
670 su2double dCD_dCL = config->GetdCD_dCL();
671 su2double dCMx_dCL = config->GetdCMx_dCL();
672 su2double dCMy_dCL = config->GetdCMy_dCL();
673 su2double dCMz_dCL = config->GetdCMz_dCL();
674 bool Fixed_CL = config->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
675
676 ForceProj_Vector = new su2double[nDim];
677
678 /*--- Compute coefficients needed for objective function evaluation. ---*/
679
680 CD = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CD();
681 CL = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CL();
682 CT = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CT();
683 CQ = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CQ();
684 invCD = 1.0/CD; CLCD2 = CL/(CD*CD);
685 invCQ = 1.0/CQ; CTRCQ2 = CT/(RefLength*CQ*CQ);
686
687 x_origin = RefOriginMoment[0]; y_origin = RefOriginMoment[1]; z_origin = RefOriginMoment[2];
688
689 /*--- Evaluate the boundary condition coefficients,
690 Since there may be more than one objective per marker, first we have to set all Force projection vectors to 0 ---*/
691
692 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker<nMarker; iMarker++) {
693 if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) != SEND_RECEIVE) &&
694 (config->GetMarker_All_Monitoring(iMarker) == YES))
695 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
696 for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++)
697 ForceProj_Vector[iDim]=0.0;
698 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
699 nodes->SetForceProj_Vector(iPoint,ForceProj_Vector);
700 }
701 }
702
703 /*--- Find the matching iMarker ---*/
704
705 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
706 Weight_ObjFunc = config->GetWeight_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
707 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
708 for (jMarker=0; jMarker<nMarker; jMarker++) {
709 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(jMarker);
710 if (Monitoring_Tag==Marker_Tag)
711 iMarker = jMarker;
712 }
713
714
715 if ((iMarker<nMarker) && (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) != SEND_RECEIVE) &&
716 (config->GetMarker_All_Monitoring(iMarker) == YES)) {
717 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
718
719 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
720
721 x = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 0);
722 y = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
723 if (nDim == 3) z = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 2);
724
725 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
726 ForceProj_Vector2 = nodes->GetForceProj_Vector(iPoint);
727 for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim;iDim++)
728 ForceProj_Vector[iDim]=ForceProj_Vector2[iDim];
729
730 switch (config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring)) {
731 case DRAG_COEFFICIENT :
732 if (nDim == 2) {
733
734 ForceProj_Vector[0] += Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha);
735 ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha);
736
737 /*--- Modification to run at a fixed CL and CM value ---*/
738
739 if (Fixed_CL) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += dCD_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] -= dCD_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
740
741 }
742 if (nDim == 3) {
743
744 ForceProj_Vector[0] += Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta);
745 ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Beta);
746 ForceProj_Vector[2] += Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta);
747
748 /*--- Modification to run at a fixed CL value ---*/
749
750 if (Fixed_CL) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += dCD_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] -= 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] -= dCD_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
751
752 }
753 break;
754 case LIFT_COEFFICIENT :
755 if (nDim == 2) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
756 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] = 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] += Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
757 break;
758 case SIDEFORCE_COEFFICIENT :
759 if (nDim == 2) { SU2_MPI::Error("This functional is not possible in 2D!!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);}
760 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Beta) * cos(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Beta); ForceProj_Vector[2] += -Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Beta) * sin(Alpha); }
761 break;
762 case INVERSE_DESIGN_PRESSURE :
763 Cp = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetCPressure(iMarker, iVertex);
764 CpTarget = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex);
765 Area = sqrt(Normal[0]*Normal[0] + Normal[1]*Normal[1]);
766 if (nDim == 3) Area = sqrt(Normal[0]*Normal[0] + Normal[1]*Normal[1] + Normal[2]*Normal[2]);
767 ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*2.0*(Cp-CpTarget)*Normal[0]/Area; ForceProj_Vector[1] += -Weight_ObjFunc*2.0*(Cp-CpTarget)*Normal[1]/Area;
768 if (nDim == 3) ForceProj_Vector[2] += -Weight_ObjFunc*2.0*(Cp-CpTarget)*Normal[2]/Area;
769 break;
770 case MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT :
771 if (nDim == 2) { SU2_MPI::Error("This functional is not possible in 2D!!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);}
772 if (nDim == 3) {
773
774 ForceProj_Vector[0] += 0.0;
775 ForceProj_Vector[1] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(z - z_origin)/RefLength;
776 ForceProj_Vector[2] += Weight_ObjFunc*(y - y_origin)/RefLength;
777
778 /*--- Modification to run at a fixed CL value ---*/
779
780 if (Fixed_CL) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += dCMx_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] -= 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] -= dCMx_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
781
782 }
783 break;
784 case MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT :
785 if (nDim == 2) { SU2_MPI::Error("This functional is not possible in 2D!!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);}
786 if (nDim == 3) {
787
788 ForceProj_Vector[0] += Weight_ObjFunc*(z - z_origin)/RefLength;
789 ForceProj_Vector[1] += 0.0;
790 ForceProj_Vector[2] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(x - x_origin)/RefLength;
791
792 /*--- Modification to run at a fixed CL value ---*/
793
794 if (Fixed_CL) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += dCMy_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] -= 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] -= dCMy_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
795
796 }
797 break;
798 case MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT :
799 if (nDim == 2) {
800
801 ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(y - y_origin)/RefLength;
802 ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*(x - x_origin)/RefLength;
803
804 /*--- Modification to run at a fixed CL and CM value ---*/
805
806 if (Fixed_CL) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += dCMz_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] -= dCMz_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
807
808 }
809 if (nDim == 3) {
810
811 ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(y - y_origin)/RefLength;
812 ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*(x - x_origin)/RefLength;
813 ForceProj_Vector[2] += 0;
814
815 /*--- Modification to run at a fixed CL value ---*/
816
817 if (Fixed_CL) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += dCMz_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*sin(Alpha); ForceProj_Vector[1] -= 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] -= dCMz_dCL*Weight_ObjFunc*cos(Alpha); }
818
819 }
820 break;
821 case EFFICIENCY :
822 if (nDim == 2) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(invCD*sin(Alpha)+CLCD2*cos(Alpha)); ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*(invCD*cos(Alpha)-CLCD2*sin(Alpha)); }
823 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(invCD*sin(Alpha)+CLCD2*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)); ForceProj_Vector[1] += -Weight_ObjFunc*CLCD2*sin(Beta); ForceProj_Vector[2] += Weight_ObjFunc*(invCD*cos(Alpha)-CLCD2*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)); }
824 break;
825 case EQUIVALENT_AREA :
826 WDrag = Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetWeightCd();
827 if (nDim == 2) { ForceProj_Vector[0] = cos(Alpha)*WDrag; ForceProj_Vector[1] = sin(Alpha)*WDrag; }
828 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*WDrag; ForceProj_Vector[1] = sin(Beta)*WDrag; ForceProj_Vector[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*WDrag; }
829 break;
830 case NEARFIELD_PRESSURE :
831 WDrag = Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetWeightCd();
832 if (nDim == 2) { ForceProj_Vector[0] = cos(Alpha)*WDrag; ForceProj_Vector[1] = sin(Alpha)*WDrag; }
833 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*WDrag; ForceProj_Vector[1] = sin(Beta)*WDrag; ForceProj_Vector[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*WDrag; }
834 break;
835 case FORCE_X_COEFFICIENT :
836 if (nDim == 2) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += Weight_ObjFunc*1.0; ForceProj_Vector[1] += 0.0; }
837 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += Weight_ObjFunc*1.0; ForceProj_Vector[1] += 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] += 0.0; }
838 break;
839 case FORCE_Y_COEFFICIENT :
840 if (nDim == 2) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*1.0; }
841 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[1] += Weight_ObjFunc*1.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] += 0.0; }
842 break;
843 case FORCE_Z_COEFFICIENT :
844 if (nDim == 2) { SU2_MPI::Error("This functional is not possible in 2D!!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);}
845 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[1] += 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] += Weight_ObjFunc*1.0; }
846 break;
847 case THRUST_COEFFICIENT :
848 if (nDim == 2) { SU2_MPI::Error("This functional is not possible in 2D!!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);}
849 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[1] += 0.0; ForceProj_Vector[2] += Weight_ObjFunc*1.0; }
850 break;
851 case TORQUE_COEFFICIENT :
852 if (nDim == 2) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += Weight_ObjFunc*(y - y_origin)/RefLength; ForceProj_Vector[1] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(x - x_origin)/RefLength; }
853 if (nDim == 3) { ForceProj_Vector[0] += Weight_ObjFunc*(y - y_origin)/RefLength; ForceProj_Vector[1] += -Weight_ObjFunc*(x - x_origin)/RefLength; ForceProj_Vector[2] += 0; }
854 break;
855 case FIGURE_OF_MERIT :
856 if (nDim == 2) { SU2_MPI::Error("This functional is not possible in 2D!!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);}
857 if (nDim == 3) {
858 ForceProj_Vector[0] += -Weight_ObjFunc*invCQ;
859 ForceProj_Vector[1] += -Weight_ObjFunc*CTRCQ2*(z - z_origin);
860 ForceProj_Vector[2] += Weight_ObjFunc*CTRCQ2*(y - y_origin);
861 }
862 break;
863
864 default :
865 break;
866 }
867
868 /*--- Store the force projection vector at this node ---*/
869
870 nodes->SetForceProj_Vector(iPoint,ForceProj_Vector);
871
872 }
873 }
874 }
875 delete [] ForceProj_Vector;
876
877}
878
879void CAdjEulerSolver::SetInitialCondition(CGeometry **geometry, CSolver ***solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned long TimeIter) {
880
881 const bool restart = config->GetRestart();
882 const bool dual_time = ((config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST) ||
883 (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND));
884
885 /*--- If restart solution, then interpolate the flow solution to
886 all the multigrid levels, this is important with the dual time strategy ---*/
887 if (restart) {
888 for (auto iMesh = 1ul; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
889 MultigridRestriction(*geometry[iMesh - 1], solver_container[iMesh - 1][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(),
890 *geometry[iMesh], solver_container[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution());
891 solver_container[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->InitiateComms(geometry[iMesh], config, SOLUTION);
892 solver_container[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->CompleteComms(geometry[iMesh], config, SOLUTION);
893 }
894 }
895
896 /*--- The value of the solution for the first iteration of the dual time ---*/
897 for (auto iMesh = 0ul; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
898 if ((TimeIter == 0) && (dual_time)) {
899 solver_container[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->Set_Solution_time_n();
900 solver_container[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->Set_Solution_time_n1();
901 }
902 }
903
904}
905
906void CAdjEulerSolver::Preprocessing(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, unsigned short iRKStep, unsigned short RunTime_EqSystem, bool Output) {
907
908 unsigned long iPoint, nonPhysicalPoints = 0;
909 su2double SharpEdge_Distance;
910 bool physical = true;
911
912 /*--- Retrieve information about the spatial and temporal integration for the
913 adjoint equations (note that the flow problem may use different methods). ---*/
914
915 bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
916 bool muscl = config->GetMUSCL_AdjFlow();
917 bool limiter = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_AdjFlow() != LIMITER::NONE);
918 bool center = (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_AdjFlow() == SPACE_CENTERED);
919 bool center_jst = (config->GetKind_Centered_AdjFlow() == CENTERED::JST);
920 bool fixed_cl = config->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
921 bool eval_dof_dcx = config->GetEval_dOF_dCX();
922
923 /*--- Update the objective function coefficient to guarantee zero gradient. ---*/
924
925 if (fixed_cl && eval_dof_dcx) { SetFarfield_AoA(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output); }
926
927 /*--- Residual initialization ---*/
928
929 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint ++) {
930
931 /*--- Get the distance form a sharp edge ---*/
932
933 SharpEdge_Distance = geometry->nodes->GetSharpEdge_Distance(iPoint);
934
935 /*--- Set the primitive variables compressible
936 adjoint variables ---*/
937
938 physical = nodes->SetPrimVar(iPoint,SharpEdge_Distance, false, config);
939
940 /* Check for non-realizable states for reporting. */
941
942 if (!physical) nonPhysicalPoints++;
943
944 /*--- Initialize the convective residual vector ---*/
945
946 if (!Output) LinSysRes.SetBlock_Zero(iPoint);
947
948 }
949
950 if ((muscl) && (iMesh == MESH_0)) {
951
952 /*--- Gradient computation for MUSCL reconstruction. ---*/
953
954 if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method_Recon() == GREEN_GAUSS)
955 SetSolution_Gradient_GG(geometry, config, true);
956 if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method_Recon() == LEAST_SQUARES)
957 SetSolution_Gradient_LS(geometry, config, true);
958 if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method_Recon() == WEIGHTED_LEAST_SQUARES)
959 SetSolution_Gradient_LS(geometry, config, true);
960
961 /*--- Limiter computation ---*/
962
963 if (limiter && !Output) SetSolution_Limiter(geometry, config);
964
965 }
966
967 /*--- Artificial dissipation for centered schemes ---*/
968
969 if (center) {
970 if ((center_jst) && (iMesh == MESH_0)) {
971 SetCentered_Dissipation_Sensor(geometry, config);
972 SetUndivided_Laplacian(geometry, config);
973 if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method() == GREEN_GAUSS) SetSolution_Gradient_GG(geometry, config);
974 if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method() == WEIGHTED_LEAST_SQUARES) SetSolution_Gradient_LS(geometry, config);
975 }
976 }
977
978 /*--- Initialize the Jacobian for implicit integration ---*/
979
980 if (implicit) Jacobian.SetValZero();
981
982 /*--- Error message ---*/
983
984 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
985#ifdef HAVE_MPI
986 unsigned long MyErrorCounter = nonPhysicalPoints; nonPhysicalPoints = 0;
987 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyErrorCounter, &nonPhysicalPoints, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
988#endif
989 if (iMesh == MESH_0) config->SetNonphysical_Points(nonPhysicalPoints);
990 }
991
992}
993
994void CAdjEulerSolver::Centered_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics **numerics_container,
995 CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, unsigned short iRKStep) {
996
997 CNumerics* numerics = numerics_container[CONV_TERM];
998
999 unsigned long iEdge, iPoint, jPoint;
1000
1001 bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1002 bool jst_scheme = ((config->GetKind_Centered_AdjFlow() == CENTERED::JST) && (iMesh == MESH_0));
1003 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
1004
1005 for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
1006
1007 /*--- Points in edge, normal, and neighbors---*/
1008
1009 iPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,0);
1010 jPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,1);
1011 numerics->SetNormal(geometry->edges->GetNormal(iEdge));
1012 numerics->SetNeighbor(geometry->nodes->GetnNeighbor(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetnNeighbor(jPoint));
1013
1014 /*--- Adjoint variables w/o reconstruction ---*/
1015
1016 numerics->SetAdjointVar(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint), nodes->GetSolution(jPoint));
1017
1018 /*--- Conservative variables w/o reconstruction ---*/
1019
1020 numerics->SetConservative(solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint),
1021 solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(jPoint));
1022
1023 numerics->SetSoundSpeed(solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint),
1024 solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSoundSpeed(jPoint));
1025 numerics->SetEnthalpy(solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetEnthalpy(iPoint),
1026 solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetEnthalpy(jPoint));
1027
1028
1029 numerics->SetLambda(solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetLambda(iPoint),
1030 solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetLambda(jPoint));
1031
1032 if (jst_scheme) {
1033 numerics->SetUndivided_Laplacian(nodes->GetUndivided_Laplacian(iPoint), nodes->GetUndivided_Laplacian(jPoint));
1034 numerics->SetSensor(nodes->GetSensor(iPoint), nodes->GetSensor(jPoint));
1035 }
1036
1037 /*--- Mesh motion ---*/
1038
1039 if (grid_movement) {
1040 numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(jPoint));
1041 }
1042
1043 /*--- Compute residuals ---*/
1044
1045 numerics->ComputeResidual(Res_Conv_i, Res_Visc_i, Res_Conv_j, Res_Visc_j,
1046 Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij, Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
1047
1048 /*--- Update convective and artificial dissipation residuals ---*/
1049
1050 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Res_Conv_i);
1051 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(jPoint, Res_Conv_j);
1052 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Res_Visc_i);
1053 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(jPoint, Res_Visc_j);
1054
1055 /*--- Implicit contribution to the residual ---*/
1056
1057 if (implicit) {
1058 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
1059 Jacobian.SubtractBlock(iPoint, jPoint, Jacobian_ij);
1060 Jacobian.SubtractBlock(jPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_ji);
1061 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(jPoint, Jacobian_jj);
1062 }
1063
1064 }
1065}

1067
1068void CAdjEulerSolver::Upwind_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
1069 CNumerics **numerics_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
1070
1071 CNumerics* numerics = numerics_container[CONV_TERM];
1072
1073 su2double Project_Grad_i, Project_Grad_j, *Limiter_i = nullptr,
1074 *Limiter_j = nullptr, *Psi_i = nullptr, *Psi_j = nullptr, *V_i, *V_j;
1075 unsigned long iEdge, iPoint, jPoint, counter_local = 0, counter_global = 0;
1076 unsigned short iDim, iVar;
1077
1078 bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1079 bool muscl = (config->GetMUSCL_AdjFlow() && (iMesh == MESH_0));
1080 bool limiter = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_AdjFlow() != LIMITER::NONE);
1081 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
1082
1083 for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
1084
1085 /*--- Points in edge and normal vectors ---*/
1086
1087 iPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,0);
1088 jPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,1);
1089 numerics->SetNormal(geometry->edges->GetNormal(iEdge));
1090
1091 /*--- Adjoint variables w/o reconstruction ---*/
1092
1093 Psi_i = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
1094 Psi_j = nodes->GetSolution(jPoint);
1095 numerics->SetAdjointVar(Psi_i, Psi_j);
1096
1097 /*--- Primitive variables w/o reconstruction ---*/
1098
1099 V_i = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
1100 V_j = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetPrimitive(jPoint);
1101 numerics->SetPrimitive(V_i, V_j);
1102
1103 /*--- Grid velocities for dynamic meshes ---*/
1104
1105 if (grid_movement) {
1106 numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(jPoint));
1107 }
1108
1109 /*--- High order reconstruction using MUSCL strategy ---*/
1110
1111 if (muscl) {
1112
1113 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1114 Vector_i[iDim] = 0.5*(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(jPoint, iDim) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, iDim));
1115 Vector_j[iDim] = 0.5*(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, iDim) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(jPoint, iDim));
1116 }
1117
1118 /*--- Adjoint variables using gradient reconstruction and limiters ---*/
1119
1120 const auto Gradient_i = nodes->GetGradient_Reconstruction(iPoint);
1121 const auto Gradient_j = nodes->GetGradient_Reconstruction(jPoint);
1122
1123 if (limiter) {
1124 Limiter_i = nodes->GetLimiter(iPoint);
1125 Limiter_j = nodes->GetLimiter(jPoint);
1126 }
1127
1128 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1129 Project_Grad_i = 0; Project_Grad_j = 0;
1130 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1131 Project_Grad_i += Vector_i[iDim]*Gradient_i[iVar][iDim];
1132 Project_Grad_j += Vector_j[iDim]*Gradient_j[iVar][iDim];
1133 }
1134 if (limiter) {
1135 Solution_i[iVar] = Psi_i[iVar] + Project_Grad_i*Limiter_i[iDim];
1136 Solution_j[iVar] = Psi_j[iVar] + Project_Grad_j*Limiter_j[iDim];
1137 }
1138 else {
1139 Solution_i[iVar] = Psi_i[iVar] + Project_Grad_i;
1140 Solution_j[iVar] = Psi_j[iVar] + Project_Grad_j;
1141 }
1142 }
1143
1144 /* Check our reconstruction for exceeding bounds on the
1145 adjoint density. */
1146
1147 su2double adj_limit = config->GetAdjointLimit();
1148 bool phi_bound_i = (fabs(Solution_i[0]) > adj_limit);
1149 bool phi_bound_j = (fabs(Solution_j[0]) > adj_limit);
1150
1151 if (phi_bound_i) nodes->SetNon_Physical(iPoint, true);
1152 else nodes->SetNon_Physical(iPoint, false);
1153
1154 if (phi_bound_j) nodes->SetNon_Physical(jPoint, true);
1155 else nodes->SetNon_Physical(jPoint, false);
1156
1157 /* Lastly, check for existing first-order points still active
1158 from previous iterations. */
1159
1160 if (nodes->GetNon_Physical(iPoint)) {
1161 counter_local++;
1162 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1163 Solution_i[iVar] = Psi_i[iVar];
1164 }
1165 if (nodes->GetNon_Physical(jPoint)) {
1166 counter_local++;
1167 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1168 Solution_j[iVar] = Psi_j[iVar];
1169 }
1170
1171 numerics->SetAdjointVar(Solution_i, Solution_j);
1172
1173 }
1174
1175 /*--- Compute the residual---*/
1176
1177 numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij, Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
1178
1179 /*--- Add and Subtract Residual ---*/
1180
1181 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
1182 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(jPoint, Residual_j);
1183
1184 /*--- Implicit contribution to the residual ---*/
1185
1186 if (implicit) {
1187 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
1188 Jacobian.SubtractBlock(iPoint, jPoint, Jacobian_ij);
1189 Jacobian.SubtractBlock(jPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_ji);
1190 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(jPoint, Jacobian_jj);
1191 }
1192
1193 }
1194
1195 /*--- Warning message about non-physical reconstructions. ---*/
1196
1197 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
1198#ifdef HAVE_MPI
1199 SU2_MPI::Reduce(&counter_local, &counter_global, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1200#else
1201 counter_global = counter_local;
1202#endif
1203 if (iMesh == MESH_0) config->SetNonphysical_Reconstr(counter_global);
1204 }
1205
1206}
1207
1208void CAdjEulerSolver::Source_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
1209 CNumerics **numerics_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
1210
1211 CNumerics* numerics = numerics_container[SOURCE_FIRST_TERM];
1212
1213 unsigned short iVar;
1214 unsigned long iPoint;
1215 bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1216 bool rotating_frame = config->GetRotating_Frame();
1217 bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
1218 // bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce() == YES);
1219 bool harmonic_balance = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::HARMONIC_BALANCE);
1220
1221 /*--- Initialize the source residual to zero ---*/
1222 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Residual[iVar] = 0.0;
1223
1224 if (rotating_frame) {
1225
1226 /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
1227 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1228
1229 /*--- Load the adjoint variables ---*/
1230 numerics->SetAdjointVar(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint),
1231 nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
1232
1233 /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
1234 numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
1235
1236 /*--- Compute the adjoint rotating frame source residual ---*/
1237 numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, config);
1238
1239 /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
1240 LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
1241
1242 /*--- Add the implicit Jacobian contribution ---*/
1243 if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_i);
1244
1245 }
1246 }
1247
1248 if (harmonic_balance) {
1249
1250 su2double Volume, Source;
1251
1252 /*--- loop over points ---*/
1253 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1254
1255 /*--- Get control volume ---*/
1256 Volume = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
1257
1258 /*--- Get stored harmonic balance source term ---*/
1259 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1260 Source = nodes->GetHarmonicBalance_Source(iPoint,iVar);
1261 Residual[iVar] = Source*Volume;
1262 }
1263
1264 /*--- Add Residual ---*/
1265 LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
1266
1267 }
1268 }
1269
1270 if (axisymmetric) {
1271
1272 /*--- Zero out Jacobian structure ---*/
1273 if (implicit) {
1274 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar ++)
1275 for (unsigned short jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar ++)
1276 Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
1277 }
1278
1279 /*--- loop over points ---*/
1280 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1281
1282 /*--- Set solution ---*/
1283 numerics->SetConservative(solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint), solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint));
1284
1285 /*--- Set adjoint variables ---*/
1286 numerics->SetAdjointVar(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint), nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
1287
1288 /*--- Set control volume ---*/
1289 numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
1290
1291 /*--- Set coordinate ---*/
1292 numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint));
1293
1294 /*--- Compute Source term Residual ---*/
1295 numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, config);
1296
1297 /*--- Add Residual ---*/
1298 LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
1299
1300 /*--- Implicit part ---*/
1301 if (implicit)
1302 Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_i);
1303
1304 }
1305 }
1306
1307 // if (gravity) {
1308 //
1309 // }
1310
1311}

1317void CAdjEulerSolver::SetCentered_Dissipation_Sensor(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
1318
1319 unsigned long iPoint;
1320 su2double SharpEdge_Distance, eps, ds, scale, Sensor, Param_Kappa_2, Param_Kappa_4;
1321
1322 eps = config->GetVenkat_LimiterCoeff()*config->GetRefElemLength();
1323 Param_Kappa_2 = config->GetKappa_2nd_AdjFlow();
1324 Param_Kappa_4 = config->GetKappa_4th_AdjFlow();
1325
1326 if (Param_Kappa_2 != 0.0) scale = 2.0 * Param_Kappa_4 / Param_Kappa_2;
1327 else scale = 0.0;
1328
1329 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
1330
1331 SharpEdge_Distance = (geometry->nodes->GetSharpEdge_Distance(iPoint) - config->GetAdjSharp_LimiterCoeff()*eps);
1332
1333 ds = 0.0;
1334 if (SharpEdge_Distance < -eps) ds = 1.0;
1335 if (fabs(SharpEdge_Distance) <= eps) ds = 1.0 - (0.5*(1.0+(SharpEdge_Distance/eps)+(1.0/PI_NUMBER)*sin(PI_NUMBER*SharpEdge_Distance/eps)));
1336 if (SharpEdge_Distance > eps) ds = 0.0;
1337
1338 Sensor = scale * ds;
1339
1340 nodes->SetSensor(iPoint,Sensor);
1341
1342 }
1343
1344 /*--- MPI parallelization ---*/
1345
1346 InitiateComms(geometry, config, SENSOR);
1347 CompleteComms(geometry, config, SENSOR);
1348
1349}
1350
1351void CAdjEulerSolver::ExplicitRK_Iteration(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
1352 CConfig *config, unsigned short iRKStep) {
1353 su2double *Residual, *Res_TruncError, Vol, Delta, Res;
1354 unsigned short iVar;
1355 unsigned long iPoint;
1356
1357 su2double RK_AlphaCoeff = config->Get_Alpha_RKStep(iRKStep);
1358
1359 SetResToZero();
1360
1361 /*--- Update the solution ---*/
1362 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1363 Vol = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
1364 Delta = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetDelta_Time(iPoint) / Vol;
1365
1366 Res_TruncError = nodes->GetResTruncError(iPoint);
1367 Residual = LinSysRes.GetBlock(iPoint);
1368
1369 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1370 Res = Residual[iVar] + Res_TruncError[iVar];
1371 nodes->AddSolution(iPoint,iVar, -Res*Delta*RK_AlphaCoeff);
1372 Residual_RMS[iVar] += Res*Res;
1373 AddRes_Max(iVar, fabs(Res), geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint));
1374 }
1375
1376 }
1377
1378 /*--- MPI solution ---*/
1379
1380 InitiateComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
1381 CompleteComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
1382
1383 /*--- Compute the root mean square residual ---*/
1384 SetResidual_RMS(geometry, config);
1385
1386}
