1388void CAdjEulerSolver::ExplicitEuler_Iteration(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config) {
1389 su2double *local_Residual, *local_Res_TruncError, Vol, Delta, Res;
1390 unsigned short iVar;
1391 unsigned long iPoint;
1392
1393 SetResToZero();
1394
1395 /*--- Update the solution ---*/
1396 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1397 Vol = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
1398 Delta = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetDelta_Time(iPoint) / Vol;
1399
1400 local_Res_TruncError = nodes->GetResTruncError(iPoint);
1401 local_Residual = LinSysRes.GetBlock(iPoint);
1402
1403 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1404 Res = local_Residual[iVar] + local_Res_TruncError[iVar];
1405 nodes->AddSolution(iPoint,iVar, -Res*Delta);
1406 Residual_RMS[iVar] += Res*Res;
1407 AddRes_Max(iVar, fabs(Res), geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint));
1408 }
1409
1410 }
1411
1412 /*--- MPI solution ---*/
1413
1414 InitiateComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
1415 CompleteComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
1416
1417 /*--- Compute the root mean square residual ---*/
1418 SetResidual_RMS(geometry, config);
1419
1420}
1421
1422void CAdjEulerSolver::ImplicitEuler_Iteration(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config) {
1423
1424 unsigned short iVar;
1425 unsigned long iPoint, total_index;
1426 su2double Delta, *local_Res_TruncError, Vol;
1427
1428 /*--- Set maximum residual to zero ---*/
1429
1430 SetResToZero();
1431
1432 /*--- Build implicit system ---*/
1433
1434 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1435
1436 /*--- Read the residual ---*/
1437
1438 local_Res_TruncError = nodes->GetResTruncError(iPoint);
1439
1440 /*--- Read the volume ---*/
1441
1442 Vol = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
1443
1444 /*--- Modify matrix diagonal to assure diagonal dominance ---*/
1445
1446 if (solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetDelta_Time(iPoint) != 0.0) {
1447 Delta = Vol / solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetDelta_Time(iPoint);
1448 Jacobian.AddVal2Diag(iPoint, Delta);
1449 }
1450 else {
1451 Jacobian.SetVal2Diag(iPoint, 1.0);
1452 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1453 total_index = iPoint*nVar + iVar;
1454 LinSysRes[total_index] = 0.0;
1455 local_Res_TruncError[iVar] = 0.0;
1456 }
1457 }
1458
1459 /*--- Right hand side of the system (-Residual) and initial guess (x = 0) ---*/
1460
1461 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1462 total_index = iPoint*nVar+iVar;
1463 LinSysRes[total_index] = -(LinSysRes[total_index] + local_Res_TruncError[iVar]);
1464 LinSysSol[total_index] = 0.0;
1465 Residual_RMS[iVar] += LinSysRes[total_index]*LinSysRes[total_index];
1466 AddRes_Max(iVar, fabs(LinSysRes[total_index]), geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint));
1467 }
1468
1469 }
1470
1471 /*--- Initialize residual and solution at the ghost points ---*/
1472
1473 for (iPoint = nPointDomain; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
1474 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1475 total_index = iPoint*nVar + iVar;
1476 LinSysRes[total_index] = 0.0;
1477 LinSysSol[total_index] = 0.0;
1478 }
1479 }
1480
1481 /*--- Solve or smooth the linear system ---*/
1482
1483 System.Solve(Jacobian, LinSysRes, LinSysSol, geometry, config);
1484
1485 /*--- Update solution (system written in terms of increments) ---*/
1486
1487 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++)
1488 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1489 nodes->AddSolution(iPoint,iVar, config->GetRelaxation_Factor_Adjoint()*LinSysSol[iPoint*nVar+iVar]);
1490 }
1491
1492 /*--- MPI solution ---*/
1493
1494 InitiateComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
1495 CompleteComms(geometry, config, SOLUTION);
1496
1497 /*--- Compute the root mean square residual ---*/
1498
1499 SetResidual_RMS(geometry, config);
1500
1501}
1502
1503void CAdjEulerSolver::Inviscid_Sensitivity(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *numerics, CConfig *config) {
1504
1505 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Neigh;
1506 unsigned short iPos, jPos;
1507 unsigned short iDim, iMarker, iNeigh;
1508 su2double *d = nullptr, *Normal = nullptr, *Psi = nullptr, *U = nullptr, Enthalpy, conspsi = 0.0, Mach_Inf,
1509 Area, *ConsPsi_Grad = nullptr,
1510 ConsPsi, d_press, grad_v, v_gradconspsi, UnitNormal[3], *GridVel = nullptr,
1511 eps, r, ru, rv, rw, rE, p, T, dp_dr, dp_dru, dp_drv,
1512 dp_drw, dp_drE, dH_dr, dH_dru, dH_drv, dH_drw, dH_drE, H, *USens, D[3][3], Dd[3], scale = 1.0;
1513 su2double RefVel2, RefDensity, Mach2Vel, *Velocity_Inf, factor;
1514 su2double Vn, SoundSpeed, *Velocity;
1515
1516 USens = new su2double[nVar];
1517 Velocity = new su2double[nDim];
1518
1519 su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
1520 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
1521 su2double RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
1522 su2double Mach_Motion = config->GetMach_Motion();
1523 unsigned short ObjFunc = config->GetKind_ObjFunc();
1524
1525 if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) scale = 1.0/12.0;
1526 else scale = 1.0;
1527
1528 /*--- Compute non-dimensional factor. For dynamic meshes, use the motion Mach
1529 number as a reference value for computing the force coefficients.
1530 Otherwise, use the freestream values,
1531 which is the standard convention. ---*/
1532
1533 if (grid_movement) {
1534 Mach2Vel = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND());
1535 RefVel2 = (Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel)*(Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel);
1536 }
1537 else {
1538 Velocity_Inf = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND();
1539 RefVel2 = 0.0;
1540 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1541 RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
1542 }
1543
1544 RefDensity = config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
1545
1546 factor = 1.0;
1547 /*-- For multi-objective problems these scaling factors are applied before solution ---*/
1548 if (config->GetnObj()==1) {
1549 factor = 1.0/(0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);
1550 if ((ObjFunc == INVERSE_DESIGN_HEATFLUX) ||
1551 (ObjFunc == TOTAL_HEATFLUX) || (ObjFunc == MAXIMUM_HEATFLUX) ||
1552 (ObjFunc == SURFACE_MASSFLOW) )
1553 factor = 1.0;
1554
1555 if ((ObjFunc == SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE) || (ObjFunc == SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE)) factor = 1.0/Area_Monitored;
1556
1557 }
1558
1559 /*--- Initialize sensitivities to zero ---*/
1560
1561 Total_Sens_Geo = 0.0;
1562 Total_Sens_Mach = 0.0;
1563 Total_Sens_AoA = 0.0;
1564 Total_Sens_Press = 0.0;
1565 Total_Sens_Temp = 0.0;
1566 Total_Sens_BPress = 0.0;
1567
1568 /*--- Loop over boundary markers to select those for Euler walls ---*/
1569
1570 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++)
1571
1572 if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == EULER_WALL)
1573
1574 /*--- Loop over points on the surface to store the auxiliary variable ---*/
1575
1576 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
1577 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1578 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
1579 Psi = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
1580 U = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint);
1581 Enthalpy = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
1582 conspsi = U[0]*Psi[0] + U[0]*Enthalpy*Psi[nDim+1];
1583 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) conspsi += U[iDim+1]*Psi[iDim+1];
1584
1585 nodes->SetAuxVar(iPoint,0,conspsi);
1586
1587 /*--- Also load the auxiliary variable for first neighbors ---*/
1588
1589 for (iNeigh = 0; iNeigh < geometry->nodes->GetnPoint(iPoint); iNeigh++) {
1590 Neigh = geometry->nodes->GetPoint(iPoint, iNeigh);
1591 Psi = nodes->GetSolution(Neigh);
1592 U = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(Neigh);
1593 Enthalpy = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetEnthalpy(Neigh);
1594 conspsi = U[0]*Psi[0] + U[0]*Enthalpy*Psi[nDim+1];
1595 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) conspsi += U[iDim+1]*Psi[iDim+1];
1596 nodes->SetAuxVar(Neigh,0,conspsi);
1597 }
1598 }
1599 }
1600
1601 /*--- Compute surface gradients of the auxiliary variable ---*/
1602
1603 SetAuxVar_Surface_Gradient(geometry, config);
1604
1605 /*--- Evaluate the shape sensitivity ---*/
1606
1607 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1608 Sens_Geo[iMarker] = 0.0;
1609
1610 if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == EULER_WALL) {
1611 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
1612 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1613 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
1614
1615 d = nodes->GetForceProj_Vector(iPoint);
1616 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1617 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
1618
1619 const auto PrimVar_Grad = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint);
1620 ConsPsi_Grad = nodes->GetAuxVarGradient(iPoint)[0];
1621 ConsPsi = nodes->GetAuxVar(iPoint);
1622
1623 d_press = 0.0; grad_v = 0.0; v_gradconspsi = 0.0;
1624 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1625
1626 /*-- Retrieve the value of the pressure gradient ---*/
1627
1628 d_press += d[iDim]*PrimVar_Grad[nDim+1][iDim];
1629
1630 /*-- Retrieve the value of the velocity gradient ---*/
1631
1632 grad_v += PrimVar_Grad[iDim+1][iDim]*ConsPsi;
1633
1634 /*-- Retrieve the value of the theta gradient ---*/
1635
1636 v_gradconspsi += solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetVelocity(iPoint, iDim) * ConsPsi_Grad[iDim];
1637
1638 /*--- Additional sensitivity term for grid movement ---*/
1639
1640 if (grid_movement) {
1641 GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
1642 v_gradconspsi -= GridVel[iDim] * ConsPsi_Grad[iDim];
1643 }
1644
1645 }
1646
1647 /*--- Compute sensitivity for each surface point ---*/
1648
1649 CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex] = (d_press + grad_v + v_gradconspsi) * Area * scale * factor;
1650
1651 /*--- If sharp edge, set the sensitivity to 0 on that region ---*/
1652
1653 if (config->GetSens_Remove_Sharp()) {
1654 eps = config->GetVenkat_LimiterCoeff()*config->GetRefElemLength();
1655 if ( geometry->nodes->GetSharpEdge_Distance(iPoint) < config->GetAdjSharp_LimiterCoeff()*eps )
1656 CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex] = 0.0;
1657 }
1658
1659 Sens_Geo[iMarker] -= CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex];
1660
1661 }
1662 }
1663
1664 Total_Sens_Geo += Sens_Geo[iMarker];
1665
1666 }
1667 }
1668
1669
1670 /*--- Farfield Sensitivity (Mach, AoA, Press, Temp), only for compressible flows ---*/
1671
1672
1673 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1674 Sens_BPress[iMarker] = 0.0;
1675 if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == OUTLET_FLOW) {
1676
1677 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
1678 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1679
1680 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
1681 Psi = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
1682 U = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint);
1683 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1684
1685 Mach_Inf = config->GetMach();
1686 if (grid_movement) Mach_Inf = config->GetMach_Motion();
1687
1688 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
1689
1690 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) UnitNormal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim]/Area;
1691
1692 Vn = 0.0;
1693 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1694 Velocity[iDim] = U[iDim+1]/U[0];
1695 Vn += UnitNormal[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
1696 }
1697
1698 SoundSpeed = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
1699 if (Vn<SoundSpeed && Vn>0) {
1700 /*TODO: MDO compatible*/
1701 Sens_BPress[iMarker]+=Psi[nDim+1]*(SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed-Vn*Vn)/(Vn*Gamma_Minus_One);
1702 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc()==SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE)
1703 Sens_BPress[iMarker]+=1;
1704 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc()==SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE) {
1705 for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++)
1706 Sens_BPress[iMarker]+=0.5*Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]/(Vn*Vn);
1707 }
1708 }
1709 }
1710 Total_Sens_BPress+= Sens_BPress[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1711 }
1712 }
1713
1714 if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == FAR_FIELD || config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == INLET_FLOW
1715 || config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SUPERSONIC_INLET || config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SUPERSONIC_OUTLET
1716 || config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW ) {
1717
1718 Sens_Mach[iMarker] = 0.0;
1719 Sens_AoA[iMarker] = 0.0;
1720 Sens_Press[iMarker] = 0.0;
1721 Sens_Temp[iMarker] = 0.0;
1722
1723 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
1724 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1725
1726 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
1727 Psi = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
1728 U = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint);
1729 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1730
1731 Mach_Inf = config->GetMach();
1732 if (grid_movement) Mach_Inf = config->GetMach_Motion();
1733
1734 r = U[0]; ru = U[1]; rv = U[2];
1735 if (nDim == 2) { rw = 0.0; rE = U[3]; }
1736 else { rw = U[3]; rE = U[4]; }
1737 p = Gamma_Minus_One*(rE-(ru*ru + rv*rv + rw*rw)/(2*r));
1738
1739 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
1740 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) UnitNormal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim]/Area;
1741
1742 H = (rE + p)/r;
1743
1744 dp_dr = Gamma_Minus_One*(ru*ru + rv*rv + rw*rw)/(2*r*r);
1745 dp_dru = -Gamma_Minus_One*ru/r;
1746 dp_drv = -Gamma_Minus_One*rv/r;
1747 if (nDim == 2) { dp_drw = 0.0; dp_drE = Gamma_Minus_One; }
1748 else { dp_drw = -Gamma_Minus_One*rw/r; dp_drE = Gamma_Minus_One; }
1749
1750 dH_dr = (-H + dp_dr)/r; dH_dru = dp_dru/r; dH_drv = dp_drv/r;
1751 if (nDim == 2) { dH_drw = 0.0; dH_drE = (1 + dp_drE)/r; }
1752 else { dH_drw = dp_drw/r; dH_drE = (1 + dp_drE)/r; }
1753
1754 if (nDim == 2) {
1755 Jacobian_j[0][0] = 0.0;
1756 Jacobian_j[1][0] = Area*UnitNormal[0];
1757 Jacobian_j[2][0] = Area*UnitNormal[1];
1758 Jacobian_j[3][0] = 0.0;
1759
1760 Jacobian_j[0][1] = (-(ru*ru)/(r*r) + dp_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (-(ru*rv)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1761 Jacobian_j[1][1] = (2*ru/r + dp_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv/r)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1762 Jacobian_j[2][1] = (dp_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (ru/r)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1763 Jacobian_j[3][1] = (dp_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[0];
1764
1765 Jacobian_j[0][2] = (-(ru*rv)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (-(rv*rv)/(r*r) + dp_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1766 Jacobian_j[1][2] = (rv/r)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (dp_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1767 Jacobian_j[2][2] = (ru/r)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (2*rv/r + dp_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1768 Jacobian_j[3][2] = (dp_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1769
1770 Jacobian_j[0][3] = (ru*dH_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv*dH_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1771 Jacobian_j[1][3] = (H + ru*dH_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv*dH_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1772 Jacobian_j[2][3] = (ru*dH_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (H + rv*dH_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1773 Jacobian_j[3][3] = (ru*dH_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv*dH_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1774 }
1775 else {
1776 Jacobian_j[0][0] = 0.0;
1777 Jacobian_j[1][0] = Area*UnitNormal[0];
1778 Jacobian_j[2][0] = Area*UnitNormal[1];
1779 Jacobian_j[3][0] = Area*UnitNormal[2];
1780 Jacobian_j[4][0] = 0.0;
1781
1782 Jacobian_j[0][1] = (-(ru*ru)/(r*r) + dp_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (-(ru*rv)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (-(ru*rw)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1783 Jacobian_j[1][1] = (2*ru/r + dp_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv/r)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (rw/r)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1784 Jacobian_j[2][1] = (dp_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (ru/r)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1785 Jacobian_j[3][1] = (dp_drw)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (ru/r)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1786 Jacobian_j[4][1] = (dp_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[0];
1787
1788 Jacobian_j[0][2] = (-(ru*rv)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (-(rv*rv)/(r*r) + dp_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (-(rv*rw)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1789 Jacobian_j[1][2] = (rv/r)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (dp_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1790 Jacobian_j[2][2] = (ru/r)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (2*rv/r + dp_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (rw/r)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1791 Jacobian_j[3][2] = (dp_drw)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (rv/r)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1792 Jacobian_j[4][2] = (dp_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[1];
1793
1794 Jacobian_j[0][3] = (-(ru*rw)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (-(rv*rw)/(r*r))*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (-(rw*rw)/(r*r) + dp_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1795 Jacobian_j[1][3] = (rw/r)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (dp_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1796 Jacobian_j[2][3] = (rw/r)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (dp_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1797 Jacobian_j[3][3] = (ru/r)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv/r)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (2*rw/r + dp_drw)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1798 Jacobian_j[4][3] = (dp_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1799
1800 Jacobian_j[0][4] = (ru*dH_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv*dH_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (rw*dH_dr)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1801 Jacobian_j[1][4] = (H + ru*dH_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv*dH_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (rw*dH_dru)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1802 Jacobian_j[2][4] = (ru*dH_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (H + rv*dH_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (rw*dH_drv)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1803 Jacobian_j[3][4] = (ru*dH_drw)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv*dH_drw)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (H + rw*dH_drw)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1804 Jacobian_j[4][4] = (ru*dH_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[0] + (rv*dH_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[1] + (rw*dH_drE)*Area*UnitNormal[2];
1805 }
1806
1807 /*--- Mach number sensitivity ---*/
1808
1809 USens[0] = 0.0; USens[1] = ru/Mach_Inf; USens[2] = rv/Mach_Inf;
1810 if (nDim == 2) { USens[3] = Gamma*Mach_Inf*p; }
1811 else { USens[3] = rw/Mach_Inf; USens[4] = Gamma*Mach_Inf*p; }
1812 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nVar; iPos++) {
1813 for (jPos = 0; jPos < nVar; jPos++) {
1814 Sens_Mach[iMarker] += Psi[iPos]*Jacobian_j[jPos][iPos]*USens[jPos];
1815 }
1816 }
1817
1818 /*--- AoA sensitivity ---*/
1819
1820 USens[0] = 0.0;
1821 if (nDim == 2) { USens[1] = -rv; USens[2] = ru; USens[3] = 0.0; }
1822 else { USens[1] = -rw; USens[2] = 0.0; USens[3] = ru; USens[4] = 0.0; }
1823 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nVar; iPos++) {
1824 for (jPos = 0; jPos < nVar; jPos++) {
1825 Sens_AoA[iMarker] += Psi[iPos]*Jacobian_j[jPos][iPos]*USens[jPos];
1826 }
1827 }
1828
1829 /*--- Pressure sensitivity ---*/
1830
1831 USens[0] = r/p; USens[1] = ru/p; USens[2] = rv/p;
1832 if (nDim == 2) { USens[3] = rE/p; }
1833 else { USens[3] = rw/p; USens[4] = rE/p; }
1834 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nVar; iPos++) {
1835 for (jPos = 0; jPos < nVar; jPos++) {
1836 Sens_Press[iMarker] += Psi[iPos]*Jacobian_j[jPos][iPos]*USens[jPos];
1837 }
1838 }
1839
1840 /*--- Temperature sensitivity ---*/
1841
1842 T = p/(r*Gas_Constant);
1843 USens[0] = -r/T; USens[1] = 0.5*ru/T; USens[2] = 0.5*rv/T;
1844 if (nDim == 2) { USens[3] = (ru*ru + rv*rv + rw*rw)/(r*T); }
1845 else { USens[3] = 0.5*rw/T; USens[4] = (ru*ru + rv*rv + rw*rw)/(r*T); }
1846 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nVar; iPos++) {
1847 for (jPos = 0; jPos < nVar; jPos++) {
1848 Sens_Temp[iMarker] += Psi[iPos]*Jacobian_j[jPos][iPos]*USens[jPos];
1849 }
1850 }
1851 }
1852 }
1853
1854 Total_Sens_Mach -= Sens_Mach[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1855 Total_Sens_AoA -= Sens_AoA[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1856 Total_Sens_Press -= Sens_Press[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1857 Total_Sens_Temp -= Sens_Temp[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1858
1859 }
1860 }
1861
1862 /*--- Explicit contribution from objective function quantity ---*/
1863
1864 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1865
1866 if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == EULER_WALL) {
1867
1868 Sens_Mach[iMarker] = 0.0;
1869 Sens_AoA[iMarker] = 0.0;
1870 Sens_Press[iMarker] = 0.0;
1871 Sens_Temp[iMarker] = 0.0;
1872
1873 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
1874 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1875
1876 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
1877
1878 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1879 p = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetPressure(iPoint);
1880
1881 Mach_Inf = config->GetMach();
1882 if (grid_movement) Mach_Inf = config->GetMach_Motion();
1883
1884 d = nodes->GetForceProj_Vector(iPoint);
1885 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
1886 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) UnitNormal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim]/Area;
1887
1888 /*--- Mach number sensitivity ---*/
1889
1890 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nDim; iPos++) Dd[iPos] = -(2.0/Mach_Inf)*d[iPos];
1891 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nDim; iPos++) Sens_Mach[iMarker] += p*Dd[iPos]*Area*UnitNormal[iPos];
1892
1893 /*--- AoA sensitivity ---*/
1894
1895 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == DRAG_COEFFICIENT ||
1896 config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == LIFT_COEFFICIENT ||
1897 config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == SIDEFORCE_COEFFICIENT ||
1898 config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == EQUIVALENT_AREA ||
1899 config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == NEARFIELD_PRESSURE) {
1900 if (nDim == 2) {
1901 D[0][0] = 0.0; D[0][1] = -1.0;
1902 D[1][0] = 1.0; D[1][1] = 0.0;
1903 }
1904 else {
1905 D[0][0] = 0.0; D[0][1] = 0.0; D[0][2] = -1.0;
1906 D[1][0] = 0.0; D[1][1] = 0.0; D[1][2] = 0.0;
1907 D[2][0] = 1.0; D[2][1] = 0.0; D[2][2] = 0.0;
1908 }
1909 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nDim; iPos++) Dd[iPos] = 0.0;
1910 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nDim; iPos++) {
1911 for (jPos = 0; jPos < nDim; jPos++)
1912 Dd[iPos] += D[iPos][jPos]*d[jPos];
1913 }
1914 }
1915
1916 /*--- Coefficients with no explicit AoA dependece ---*/
1917
1918 else {
1919 for (iPos = 0; iPos<nDim; iPos++) Dd[iPos] = 0.0;
1920 }
1921
1922 for (iPos = 0; iPos < nDim; iPos++)
1923 Sens_AoA[iMarker] += p*Dd[iPos]*Area*UnitNormal[iPos];
1924
1925 /*--- Pressure sensitivity ---*/
1926
1927 for (iPos = 0; iPos<nDim; iPos++) Dd[iPos] = -(1/p)*d[iPos];
1928 for (iPos = 0; iPos<nDim; iPos++)
1929 Sens_Press[iMarker] += p*Dd[iPos]*Area*UnitNormal[iPos];
1930
1931 /*--- Temperature sensitivity ---*/
1932
1933 for (iPos = 0; iPos<nDim; iPos++) Dd[iPos] = 0.0;
1934 for (iPos = 0; iPos<nDim; iPos++)
1935 Sens_Temp[iMarker] += p*Dd[iPos]*Area*UnitNormal[iPos];
1936
1937 }
1938 }
1939
1940 Total_Sens_Mach += Sens_Mach[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1941 Total_Sens_AoA += Sens_AoA[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1942 Total_Sens_Press += Sens_Press[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1943 Total_Sens_Temp += Sens_Temp[iMarker] * scale * factor;
1944
1945 }
1946 }
1947
1948
1949#ifdef HAVE_MPI
1950
1951 su2double MyTotal_Sens_Geo = Total_Sens_Geo; Total_Sens_Geo = 0.0;
1952 su2double MyTotal_Sens_Mach = Total_Sens_Mach; Total_Sens_Mach = 0.0;
1953 su2double MyTotal_Sens_AoA = Total_Sens_AoA; Total_Sens_AoA = 0.0;
1954 su2double MyTotal_Sens_Press = Total_Sens_Press; Total_Sens_Press = 0.0;
1955 su2double MyTotal_Sens_Temp = Total_Sens_Temp; Total_Sens_Temp = 0.0;
1956 su2double MyTotal_Sens_BPress = Total_Sens_BPress; Total_Sens_BPress = 0.0;
1957
1958 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotal_Sens_Geo, &Total_Sens_Geo, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1959 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotal_Sens_Mach, &Total_Sens_Mach, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1960 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotal_Sens_AoA, &Total_Sens_AoA, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1961 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotal_Sens_Press, &Total_Sens_Press, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1962 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotal_Sens_Temp, &Total_Sens_Temp, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1963 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotal_Sens_BPress, &Total_Sens_BPress, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1964
1965#endif
1966
1967 delete [] USens;
1968 delete [] Velocity;
1969
1970}
1971
1972void CAdjEulerSolver::Smooth_Sensitivity(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *numerics, CConfig *config) {
1973 unsigned short iMarker;
1974 unsigned long iVertex, jVertex, nVertex, iPoint;
1975 su2double **A, *b, Sens, *ArchLength, *Coord_begin, *Coord_end, dist;
1976
1977 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1978 if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == EULER_WALL) {
1979 nVertex = geometry->nVertex[iMarker];
1980
1981 /*--- Allocate the linear system ---*/
1982
1983 A = new su2double* [nVertex];
1984 b = new su2double [nVertex];
1985 ArchLength = new su2double [nVertex];
1986 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
1987 A[iVertex] = new su2double [nVertex];
1988 }
1989
1990 /*--- Initialization ---*/
1991
1992 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
1993 b[iVertex] = 0.0; ArchLength[iVertex] = 0.0;
1994 for (jVertex = 0; jVertex < nVertex; jVertex++)
1995 A[iVertex][jVertex] = 0.0;
1996 }
1997
1998 /*--- Set the arch length ---*/
1999
2000 ArchLength[0] = 0.0;
2001 for (iVertex = 1; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
2002 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex-1]->GetNode();
2003 Coord_begin = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
2004 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2005 Coord_end = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
2006 dist = sqrt (pow( Coord_end[0]-Coord_begin[0], 2.0) + pow( Coord_end[1]-Coord_begin[1], 2.0));
2007 ArchLength[iVertex] = ArchLength[iVertex-1] + dist;
2008 }
2009
2010 /*--- Remove the trailing edge effect ---*/
2011
2012 su2double MinPosSens = 0.0; su2double MinNegSens = 0.0;
2013 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
2014 Sens = CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex];
2015 if (ArchLength[iVertex] > ArchLength[nVertex-1]*0.01) { MinNegSens = Sens; break; }
2016 }
2017
2018 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
2019 Sens = CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex];
2020 if (ArchLength[iVertex] > ArchLength[nVertex-1]*0.99) { MinPosSens = Sens; break; }
2021 }
2022
2023 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
2024 if (ArchLength[iVertex] < ArchLength[nVertex-1]*0.01)
2025 CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex] = MinNegSens;
2026 if (ArchLength[iVertex] > ArchLength[nVertex-1]*0.99)
2027 CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex] = MinPosSens;
2028 }
2029
2030 /*--- Set the right hand side of the system ---*/
2031
2032 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
2033 b[iVertex] = CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex];
2034 }
2035
2036 /*--- Set the mass matrix ---*/
2037
2038 su2double Coeff = 0.0, BackDiff = 0.0, ForwDiff = 0.0, CentDiff = 0.0;
2039 su2double epsilon = 5E-5;
2040 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++) {
2041
2042 if ((iVertex != nVertex-1) && (iVertex != 0)) {
2043 BackDiff = (ArchLength[iVertex]-ArchLength[iVertex-1]);
2044 ForwDiff = (ArchLength[iVertex+1]-ArchLength[iVertex]);
2045 CentDiff = (ArchLength[iVertex+1]-ArchLength[iVertex-1]);
2046 }
2047 if (iVertex == nVertex-1) {
2048 BackDiff = (ArchLength[nVertex-1]-ArchLength[nVertex-2]);
2049 ForwDiff = (ArchLength[0]-ArchLength[nVertex-1]);
2050 CentDiff = (ArchLength[0]-ArchLength[nVertex-2]);
2051 }
2052 if (iVertex == 0) {
2053 BackDiff = (ArchLength[0]-ArchLength[nVertex-1]);
2054 ForwDiff = (ArchLength[1]-ArchLength[0]);
2055 CentDiff = (ArchLength[1]-ArchLength[nVertex-1]);
2056 }
2057
2058 Coeff = epsilon*2.0/(BackDiff*ForwDiff*CentDiff);
2059
2060 A[iVertex][iVertex] = Coeff*CentDiff;
2061
2062 if (iVertex != 0) A[iVertex][iVertex-1] = -Coeff*ForwDiff;
2063 else A[iVertex][nVertex-1] = -Coeff*ForwDiff;
2064
2065 if (iVertex != nVertex-1) A[iVertex][iVertex+1] = -Coeff*BackDiff;
2066 else A[iVertex][0] = -Coeff*BackDiff;
2067
2068 }
2069
2070 /*--- Add the gradient value in the main diagonal ---*/
2071
2072 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++)
2073 A[iVertex][iVertex] += 1.0;
2074
2075 /*--- Dirichlet boundary condition ---*/
2076
2077 unsigned long iVertex = SU2_TYPE::Int(nVertex/2);
2078 A[iVertex][iVertex] = 1.0;
2079 A[iVertex][iVertex+1] = 0.0;
2080 A[iVertex][iVertex-1] = 0.0;
2081
2082 Gauss_Elimination(A, b, (unsigned short)nVertex);
2083
2084 /*--- Set the new value of the sensitiviy ---*/
2085
2086 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++)
2087 CSensitivity[iMarker][iVertex] = b[iVertex];
2088
2089 /*--- Deallocate the linear system ---*/
2090
2091 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex; iVertex++)
2092 delete [] A[iVertex];
2093 delete [] A;
2094 delete [] b;
2095 delete [] ArchLength;
2096
2097 }
2098 }
2099
2100
2101}
2102
2103void CAdjEulerSolver::SetFarfield_AoA(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
2104 CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
2105
2106 unsigned long Iter_Fixed_CL = config->GetUpdate_AoA_Iter_Limit();
2107 unsigned long InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
2108 bool Update_AoA = false;
2109 su2double dCL_dAlpha = config->GetdCL_dAlpha()*180.0/PI_NUMBER;
2110 //unsigned long Update_Alpha = config->GetUpdate_Alpha();
2111
2112 //if (ExtIter == 0) AoA_Counter = 0;
2113
2114 /*--- Only the fine mesh level should check the convergence criteria ---*/
2115
2116 if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && Output) {
2117
2118 /*--- Initialize the update flag to false ---*/
2119
2120 Update_AoA = false;
2121
2122 /*--- Reevaluate the lift derivative with respect to Angle of Attack
2123 at a fix number of iterations ---*/
2124
2125 if ((InnerIter % Iter_Fixed_CL == 0) && (InnerIter != 0)) {
2126 //AoA_Counter++;
2127 //if ((AoA_Counter <= Update_Alpha)) Update_AoA = true;
2128 Update_AoA = true;
2129 }
2130
2131 /*--- Store the update boolean for use on other mesh levels in the MG ---*/
2132
2133 config->SetUpdate_AoA(Update_AoA);
2134
2135 }
2136
2137 else {
2138 Update_AoA = config->GetUpdate_AoA();
2139 }
2140
2141 /*--- If we are within two digits of convergence in the CL coefficient,
2142 compute an updated value for the AoA at the farfield. We are iterating
2143 on the AoA in order to match the specified fixed lift coefficient. ---*/
2144
2145 if (Update_AoA && Output) {
2146
2147 /*--- Retrieve the old ACoeff ---*/
2148
2149 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == DRAG_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff_old = config->GetdCD_dCL();
2150 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff_old = config->GetdCMx_dCL();
2151 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff_old = config->GetdCMy_dCL();
2152 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff_old = config->GetdCMz_dCL();
2153 else ACoeff_old = 0.0;
2154
2155 /*--- Estimate the increment in the A coeff, (note that the slope is negative, a decrease in
2156 * the CL derivative requires an increase in the A coeff ---*/
2157
2158 /*--- A good estimation to d(dOF/dalpha)/dA_coeff is dCL_dAlpha ---*/
2159
2160 ACoeff_inc = (1.0/dCL_dAlpha)*Total_Sens_AoA;
2161
2162 /*--- Compute a new value for the A coeff based on the fine mesh only (radians)---*/
2163
2164 if (iMesh == MESH_0) { ACoeff = ACoeff_old + ACoeff_inc; }
2165 else {
2166 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == DRAG_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff = config->GetdCD_dCL();
2167 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff = config->GetdCMx_dCL();
2168 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff = config->GetdCMy_dCL();
2169 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT) ACoeff = config->GetdCMz_dCL();
2170 else ACoeff = 0.0;
2171 }
2172
2173 /*--- Only the fine mesh stores the updated values for ACoeff in config ---*/
2174
2175 if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
2176 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == DRAG_COEFFICIENT) config->SetdCD_dCL(ACoeff);
2177 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT) config->SetdCMx_dCL(ACoeff);
2178 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT) config->SetdCMy_dCL(ACoeff);
2179 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT) config->SetdCMz_dCL(ACoeff);
2180 else { config->SetdCD_dCL(0.0); config->SetdCMx_dCL(0.0); config->SetdCMy_dCL(0.0); config->SetdCMz_dCL(0.0); }
2181 }
2182
2183 /*--- Compute the adjoint boundary condition ---*/
2184
2185 SetForceProj_Vector(geometry, solver_container, config);
2186
2187 }
2188
2189 /*--- Output some information to the console with the headers ---*/
2190
2191 bool write_heads = ((InnerIter % Iter_Fixed_CL == 0) && (InnerIter != 0));
2192 if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (iMesh == MESH_0) && write_heads && Output) {
2193 cout.precision(7);
2194 cout.setf(ios::fixed, ios::floatfield);
2195 cout << endl << "-------------------------- Adjoint Fixed CL Mode -------------------------" << endl;
2196 cout << "Target dCL/dAlpha: 0.0 (1/deg), current dCL/dAlpha: " << Total_Sens_AoA*PI_NUMBER/180;
2197 if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == DRAG_COEFFICIENT) cout << " (1/deg), current dCD/dCL: " << config->GetdCD_dCL() <<" "<< endl;
2198 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT) cout << " (1/deg), current dCMx/dCL: " << config->GetdCMx_dCL() <<" "<< endl;
2199 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT) cout << " (1/deg), current dCMy/dCL: " << config->GetdCMy_dCL() <<" "<< endl;
2200 else if (config->GetKind_ObjFunc() == MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT) cout << " (1/deg), current dCMz/dCL: " << config->GetdCMz_dCL() <<" "<< endl;
2201 else cout << endl;
2202 cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl << endl;
2203 }
2204
2205
2206}

2209void CAdjEulerSolver::BC_Euler_Wall(CGeometry *geometry,
2210 CSolver **solver_container,
2211 CNumerics *conv_numerics,
2212 CNumerics *visc_numerics,
2213 CConfig *config,
2214 unsigned short val_marker) {
2215
2216 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
2217 su2double *d = nullptr, *Normal, *U, *Psi_Aux, ProjVel = 0.0, bcn, vn = 0.0, Area, *UnitNormal;
2218 su2double *Velocity, *Psi, Enthalpy = 0.0, sq_vel, phin, phis1, phis2;
2219 unsigned short iDim, iVar, jDim;
2220
2221 bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
2222 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
2223
2224 UnitNormal = new su2double[nDim];
2225 Velocity = new su2double[nDim];
2226 Psi = new su2double[nVar];
2227
2228 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
2229 iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2230
2231 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2232 Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
2233
2234 /*--- Create a copy of the adjoint solution ---*/
2235 Psi_Aux = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
2236 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Psi[iVar] = Psi_Aux[iVar];
2237
2238 /*--- Flow solution ---*/
2239 U = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint);
2240
2241 /*--- Read the value of the objective function ---*/
2242 d = nodes->GetForceProj_Vector(iPoint);
2243
2244 /*--- Normal vector computation ---*/
2245 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
2246 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) UnitNormal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim]/Area;
2247
2248 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2249 Velocity[iDim] = U[iDim+1] / U[0];
2250
2251 Enthalpy = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
2252 sq_vel = 0.5*solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetVelocity2(iPoint);
2253
2254 /*--- Compute projections ---*/
2255 ProjVel = 0.0; bcn = 0.0; vn = 0.0; phin = 0.0;
2256 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2257 ProjVel -= Velocity[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
2258 bcn += d[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2259 vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2260 phin += Psi[iDim+1]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2261 }
2262
2263 /*--- Extra boundary term for grid movement ---*/
2264 if (grid_movement) {
2265 su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
2266 su2double *GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
2267 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2268 ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2269 phin -= Psi[nVar-1]*ProjGridVel;
2270 }
2271
2272 /*--- Introduce the boundary condition ---*/
2273 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2274 Psi[iDim+1] -= ( phin - bcn ) * UnitNormal[iDim];
2275
2276 /*--- Inner products after introducing BC (Psi has changed) ---*/
2277 phis1 = 0.0; phis2 = Psi[0] + Enthalpy * Psi[nVar-1];
2278 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2279 phis1 -= Normal[iDim]*Psi[iDim+1];
2280 phis2 += Velocity[iDim]*Psi[iDim+1];
2281 }
2282
2283 /*--- Flux of the Euler wall ---*/
2284 Residual[0] = ProjVel * Psi[0] - phis2 * ProjVel + phis1 * Gamma_Minus_One * sq_vel;
2285 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2286 Residual[iDim+1] = ProjVel * Psi[iDim+1] - phis2 * Normal[iDim] - phis1 * Gamma_Minus_One * Velocity[iDim];
2287 Residual[nVar-1] = ProjVel * Psi[nVar-1] + phis1 * Gamma_Minus_One;
2288
2289 /*--- Flux adjustment for grid movement ---*/
2290 if (grid_movement) {
2291 su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
2292 su2double *GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
2293 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2294 ProjGridVel -= GridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
2295 Residual[0] -= ProjGridVel*Psi[0];
2296 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2297 Residual[iDim+1] -= ProjGridVel*Psi[iDim+1];
2298 Residual[nVar-1] -= ProjGridVel*Psi[nVar-1];
2299 }
2300
2301 if (implicit) {
2302
2303 /*--- Adjoint density ---*/
2304 Jacobian_ii[0][0] = 0.0;
2305 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2306 Jacobian_ii[0][iDim+1] = -ProjVel * (Velocity[iDim] - UnitNormal[iDim] * vn);
2307 Jacobian_ii[0][nVar-1] = -ProjVel * Enthalpy;
2308
2309 /*--- Adjoint velocities ---*/
2310 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2311 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][0] = -Normal[iDim];
2312 for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim++)
2313 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][jDim+1] = -ProjVel*(UnitNormal[jDim]*UnitNormal[iDim] - Normal[iDim] * (Velocity[jDim] - UnitNormal[jDim] * vn));
2314 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][iDim+1] += ProjVel;
2315 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][nVar-1] = -Normal[iDim] * Enthalpy;
2316 }
2317
2318 /*--- Adjoint energy ---*/
2319 Jacobian_ii[nVar-1][0] = 0.0;
2320 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2321 Jacobian_ii[nVar-1][iDim+1] = 0.0;
2322 Jacobian_ii[nVar-1][nVar-1] = ProjVel;
2323
2324 /*--- Jacobian contribution due to grid movement ---*/
2325 if (grid_movement) {
2326 su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
2327 su2double *GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
2328 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2329 ProjGridVel -= GridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
2330 Jacobian_ii[0][0] -= ProjGridVel;
2331 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2332 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][iDim+1] -= ProjGridVel;
2333 Jacobian_ii[nVar-1][nVar-1] -= ProjGridVel;
2334 }
2335
2336 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
2337
2338 }
2339
2340 /*--- Update residual ---*/
2341 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual);
2342
2343 }
2344 }
2345
2346 delete [] Velocity;
2347 delete [] UnitNormal;
2348 delete [] Psi;
2349
2350}

2353 CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {

2355 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
2356 su2double *Normal, ProjVel = 0.0, vn = 0.0, Area, *UnitNormal,
2357 *Psi_domain, *Psi_sym, *Velocity, Enthalpy = 0.0,
2358 sq_vel, phin, phis1, phis2;

2369
2370 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {

2373
2374 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2375

2384

2386
2387 /*--- Retrieve flow variables ---*/
2388
2389 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2390 Velocity[iDim] = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetVelocity(iPoint, iDim);
2391
2392 Enthalpy = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);

2394

2396
2397 ProjVel = 0.0; vn = 0.0; phin = 0.0;
2398 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2399 ProjVel -= Velocity[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
2400 vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2401 phin += Psi_domain[iDim+1]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2402 }
2403
2404 /*--- Grid Movement ---*/
2405
2406 if (grid_movement) {
2407 su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
2408 su2double *GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
2409 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2410 ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2411 }
2412 phin -= Psi_domain[nVar-1]*ProjGridVel;
2413 }
2414
2415 /*--- Introduce the boundary condition ---*/
2416
2417 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2418 Psi_domain[iDim+1] -= phin * UnitNormal[iDim];
2419
2420 /*--- Inner products after introducing BC (Psi has changed) ---*/
2421
2422 phis1 = 0.0; phis2 = Psi_domain[0] + Enthalpy * Psi_domain[nVar-1];
2423 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2424 phis1 -= Normal[iDim]*Psi_domain[iDim+1];
2425 phis2 += Velocity[iDim]*Psi_domain[iDim+1];
2426 }
2427
2428 /*--- Flux of the Euler wall ---*/
2429
2430 Residual_i[0] = ProjVel * Psi_domain[0] - phis2 * ProjVel + phis1 * Gamma_Minus_One * sq_vel;
2431 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2432 Residual_i[iDim+1] = ProjVel * Psi_domain[iDim+1] - phis2 * Normal[iDim] - phis1 * Gamma_Minus_One * Velocity[iDim];
2433 Residual_i[nVar-1] = ProjVel * Psi_domain[nVar-1] + phis1 * Gamma_Minus_One;
2434
2435 /*--- Grid Movement ---*/
2436
2437 if (grid_movement) {

2439 su2double *GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
2440 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)

2443 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2444 Residual_i[iDim+1] -= ProjGridVel*Psi_domain[iDim+1];
2445 Residual_i[nVar-1] -= ProjGridVel*Psi_domain[nVar-1];
2446 }
2447
2448 /*--- Update residual ---*/
2449
2450 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
2451
2452 /*--- Implicit stuff ---*/
2453
2454 if (implicit) {
2455
2456 /*--- Adjoint density ---*/
2457
2458 Jacobian_ii[0][0] = 0.0;
2459 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2460 Jacobian_ii[0][iDim+1] = -ProjVel * (Velocity[iDim] - UnitNormal[iDim] * vn);
2461 Jacobian_ii[0][nVar-1] = -ProjVel * Enthalpy;
2462
2463 /*--- Adjoint velocities ---*/
2464
2465 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {

2469 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][iDim+1] += ProjVel;
2470 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][nVar-1] = -Normal[iDim] * Enthalpy;
2471 }

2474
2475 Jacobian_ii[nVar-1][0] = 0.0;
2476 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)

2481

2485 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2486 ProjGridVel -= GridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
2487 Jacobian_ii[0][0] -= ProjGridVel;
2488 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2489 Jacobian_ii[iDim+1][iDim+1] -= ProjGridVel;
2490 Jacobian_ii[nVar-1][nVar-1] -= ProjGridVel;

2497 }

2499 }
2500 }

2510void CAdjEulerSolver::BC_Far_Field(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
2511
2512 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
2513 unsigned short iVar, iDim;
2514 su2double *Normal, *V_domain, *V_infty, *Psi_domain, *Psi_infty;
2515

2517 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
2518
2519 Normal = new su2double[nDim];

2521
2522 /*--- Loop over all the vertices ---*/
2523
2524 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
2525 iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2526
2527 /*--- If the node belongs to the domain ---*/
2528
2529 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2530
2531 /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
2532
2533 Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
2534
2535 /*--- Set the normal vector ---*/

2566 conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij, Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
2567

2569
2570 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
2571

2573

2575 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);

2578

2586 visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);

2589

2592

2600
2601 /*--- Update adjoint viscous residual ---*/
2602
2603 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);

2605 if (implicit)
2606 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);

2617void CAdjEulerSolver::BC_Supersonic_Inlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,

2632 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
2633 iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2634
2635 /*--- Check that the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
2636
2637 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2638
2639 /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
2640
2641 geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
2642 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
2643 conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
2644
2645 /*--- Allocate the value at the inlet ---*/

2648

2650

2652

2656 Psi_domain[iVar] = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iVar);
2657
2658 /*--- Construct the flow & adjoint states at the inlet ---*/
2659 /*--- Supersonic Inlet: All characteristic are exiting: using nearest neighbor to set value ---*/
2660 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
2661 Psi_inlet[iVar] = Psi_domain[iVar];

2666 conv_numerics->SetAdjointVar(Psi_domain, Psi_inlet);
2667
2668 /*--- Grid Movement ---*/
2669
2670 if (grid_movement)
2671 conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
2672 geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
2673
2674 /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
2675
2676 conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij,
2677 Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
2678
2679 /*--- Add and Subtract Residual ---*/
2680
2681 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
2682
2683 /*--- Implicit contribution to the residual ---*/
2684
2685 if (implicit)
2686 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
2687
2688 /*--- Viscous residual contribution, it doesn't work ---*/
2689
2690 if (config->GetViscous()) {
2691
2692 /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
2693
2694 Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
2695
2696 /*--- Points in edge, coordinates and normal vector---*/
2697
2698 su2double Coord_Reflected[3];

2700 geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
2701 visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
2702 visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
2703
2704 /*--- Conservative variables w/o reconstruction and adjoint variables w/o reconstruction---*/
2705
2706 visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
2707 visc_numerics->SetAdjointVar(Psi_domain, Psi_inlet);
2708
2709 /*--- Gradient and limiter of Adjoint Variables ---*/
2710
2711 visc_numerics->SetAdjointVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient(iPoint));
2712
2713 /*--- Compute residual ---*/
2714
2715 visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij, Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
2716
2717 /*--- Update adjoint viscous residual ---*/
2718
2719 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
2720
2721 if (implicit)
2722 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
2723
2724 }
2725 }
2726 }
2727
2728 /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
2729

2731 delete [] Psi_domain; delete [] Psi_inlet;

2853void CAdjEulerSolver::BC_Inlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
2854
2855 unsigned short iVar, iDim;
2856 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
2857 su2double Velocity[3], bcn, phin, Area, UnitNormal[3],
2858 ProjGridVel, *GridVel;
2859 su2double *V_inlet, *V_domain, *Normal, *Psi_domain, *Psi_inlet;
2860
2861 INLET_TYPE Kind_Inlet = config->GetKind_Inlet();
2862 bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
2863 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
2864 string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
2865
2866 Normal = new su2double[nDim];

2868
2869 /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
2870
2871 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
2872 iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2873
2874 /*--- Check that the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
2875

2877

2880 geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);

2882 conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);

2884 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
2885
2886 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2887 UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;

2900 Psi_domain[iVar] = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iVar);
2901
2902 /*--- Construct the flow & adjoint states at the inlet ---*/
2903
2904 /*--- Subsonic, compressible inflow: first build the flow state
2905 using the same method as the direct problem. Then, based on
2906 those conservative values, compute the characteristic-based
2907 adjoint boundary condition. The boundary update to be applied
2908 depends on whether total conditions or mass flow are specified. ---*/
2909

2911
2912 /*--- Total properties have been specified at the inlet. ---*/
2913 case INLET_TYPE::TOTAL_CONDITIONS:
2914

2916 but should be replaced with derived expression for this type of
2917 inlet. ---*/
2918 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
2919 Psi_inlet[iVar] = 0.0;
2920
2921 break;
2922
2923 /*--- Mass flow has been specified at the inlet. ---*/
2924 case INLET_TYPE::MASS_FLOW:
2925
2926 /*--- Get primitives from current inlet state. ---*/
2927 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2928 Velocity[iDim] = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetVelocity(iPoint, iDim);
2929
2930 /*--- Retrieve current adjoint solution values at the boundary ---*/
2931 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
2932 Psi_inlet[iVar] = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iVar);
2933
2934 /*--- Some terms needed for the adjoint BC ---*/
2935 bcn = 0.0; phin = 0.0;
2936 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2937 bcn -= (Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One)*Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2938 phin += Psi_domain[iDim+1]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2939 }
2940
2941 /*--- Extra boundary term for grid movement ---*/
2942 if (grid_movement) {
2943 ProjGridVel = 0.0;
2944 GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
2945 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2946 ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
2947 bcn -= (1.0/Gamma_Minus_One)*ProjGridVel;
2948 }
2949
2950 /*--- Impose value for PsiE based on hand-derived expression. ---*/
2951 Psi_inlet[nVar-1] = -phin*(1.0/bcn);
2952
2953 break;
2954
2955 default:
2956 SU2_MPI::Error("Unsupported INLET_TYPE.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
2957 break;
2958 }
2959
2960
2961 /*--- Set the flow and adjoint states in the solver ---*/
2962
2963 conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
2964 conv_numerics->SetAdjointVar(Psi_domain, Psi_inlet);
2965
2966 /*--- Grid Movement ---*/
2967
2968 if (grid_movement)
2969 conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
2970 geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
2971
2972 /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
2973
2974 conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij,
2975 Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
2976
2977 /*--- Add and Subtract Residual ---*/
2978
2979 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
2980
2981 /*--- Implicit contribution to the residual ---*/
2982
2983 if (implicit)
2984 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
2985
2986 /*--- Viscous residual contribution, it doesn't work ---*/
2987
2988 if (config->GetViscous()) {
2989 /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
2990
2991 Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
2992
2993 /*--- Points in edge, coordinates and normal vector---*/
2994
2995 su2double Coord_Reflected[3];
2996 GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
2997 geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
2998 visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
2999 visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
3000
3001 /*--- Conservative variables w/o reconstruction and adjoint variables w/o reconstruction---*/
3002
3003 visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
3004 visc_numerics->SetAdjointVar(Psi_domain, Psi_inlet);
3005
3006 /*--- Gradient and limiter of Adjoint Variables ---*/
3007
3008 visc_numerics->SetAdjointVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient(iPoint));
3009
3010 /*--- Compute residual ---*/
3011
3012 visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij, Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
3013
3014 /*--- Update adjoint viscous residual ---*/
3015
3016 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
3017
3018 if (implicit)
3019 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
3020
3021 }
3022 }

3032void CAdjEulerSolver::BC_Outlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
3033
3034 unsigned short iVar, iDim;
3035 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
3036 su2double Pressure=0.0, P_Exit=0.0, Velocity2 = 0.0, Area=0.0, Density=0.0,
3037 Vn = 0.0, SoundSpeed = 0.0, Vn_Exit=0.0, ProjGridVel = 0.0,
3038 Riemann=0.0, Entropy=0.0, Vn_rel=0.0;
3039 su2double Velocity[3], UnitNormal[3];
3040 su2double *V_outlet, *V_domain, *Psi_domain, *Psi_outlet, *Normal;
3041 su2double a1=0.0, a2=0.0; /*Placeholder terms to simplify expressions/ repeated terms*/
3042 /*Gradient terms for the generalized boundary */
3043 su2double density_gradient=0.0, pressure_gradient=0.0, velocity_gradient=0.0;
3044
3045 bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
3046 bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
3047 su2double Weight_ObjFunc = 1.0;
3048 string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
3049 string Monitoring_Tag;
3050 unsigned short jMarker=0, iMarker_Monitoring=0;
3051
3052 Psi_domain = new su2double [nVar]; Psi_outlet = new su2double [nVar];
3053 Normal = new su2double[nDim];
3054
3055 /*--- Identify marker monitoring index ---*/
3056 for (jMarker = 0; jMarker < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); jMarker++) {
3057 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(jMarker);
3058 if (Monitoring_Tag==Marker_Tag)
3059 iMarker_Monitoring = jMarker;
3060 }
3061
3062 Weight_ObjFunc = config->GetWeight_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
3063
3064 /*--- Loop over all the vertices ---*/
3065
3066 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
3067 iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3068
3069 /*--- If the node belong to the domain ---*/
3070
3071 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
3072
3073 /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
3074
3075 geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
3076 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
3077 conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
3078
3079 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
3080
3081 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3082 UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
3083
3084 /*--- Set the normal point ---*/
3085
3086 Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
3087
3088 su2double Coord_Reflected[3];
3089 GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
3090 geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
3091 conv_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
3092
3093 /*--- Allocate the value at the outlet ---*/
3094
3095 V_outlet = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
3096
3097 /*--- Retrieve solution at the boundary node ---*/
3098
3099 V_domain = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
3100
3101 /*--- Adjoint flow solution at the boundary ---*/
3102
3103 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
3104 Psi_domain[iVar] = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iVar);
3105
3106 /*--- Construct the flow & adjoint states at the outlet ---*/
3107
3108 /*--- Retrieve the specified back pressure for this outlet, Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
3109
3110 P_Exit = config->GetOutlet_Pressure(Marker_Tag);
3111 P_Exit = P_Exit/config->GetPressure_Ref();
3112
3113 /*--- Check whether the flow is supersonic at the exit. The type
3114 of boundary update depends on this. ---*/
3115
3116 Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
3117 Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
3118 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3119 Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
3120 Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
3121 Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
3122 }
3123 /*--- Extra boundary term for grid movement ---*/
3124 if (grid_movement) {
3125 su2double *GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
3126 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3127 ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
3128 }
3129
3130 Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
3131 SoundSpeed = sqrt(Pressure*Gamma/Density);
3132
3133 /*--- Set Adjoint variables to 0 initially ---*/
3134 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
3135 Psi_outlet[iVar] = 0.0;
3136 }
3137
3138 if (Vn > SoundSpeed) {
3139 /*--- Objective-dependent additions to energy term ---*/
3140 Vn_Exit = Vn; /* Vn_Exit comes from Reiman conditions in subsonic case*/
3141 Vn_rel = Vn_Exit-ProjGridVel;
3142 /* Repeated term */
3143 a1 = Gamma_Minus_One/(Vn_rel*Vn_rel-SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed);
3144
3145 switch (config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring)) {
3146 case SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE:
3147 /*--- Total Pressure term. NOTE: this is AREA averaged
3148 * Additional terms are added later (as they are common between subsonic,
3149 * supersonic equations) ---*/
3150 Velocity2 = 0.0;
3151 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3152 Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
3153 }
3154 a2 = Pressure*(Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One)*pow((1.0+Gamma_Minus_One*Density*Velocity2/(2.0*Gamma*Pressure)),1.0/Gamma_Minus_One);
3155 density_gradient = a2*(Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2/(2.0*Gamma*Pressure));
3156 velocity_gradient = 0.0;
3157 for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++)
3158 velocity_gradient+=a2*Gamma_Minus_One*Density/(Gamma*Pressure)*Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
3159 pressure_gradient = a2*(-Gamma_Minus_One*Density*Velocity2/(2.0*Gamma*pow(Pressure,2.0)))+pow((1.0+Gamma_Minus_One*Density*Velocity2/(2.0*Gamma*Pressure)),(Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One));
3160 Psi_outlet[nDim+1]+=Weight_ObjFunc*a1*(density_gradient/Vn_rel+pressure_gradient*Vn_rel-velocity_gradient/Density);
3161 break;
3162 case SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE:
3163 /*Area averaged static pressure*/
3164 /*--- Note: further terms are NOT added later for this case, only energy term is modified ---*/
3165 Psi_outlet[nDim+1]+=Weight_ObjFunc*(a1*Vn_Exit);
3166 break;
3167 default:
3168 break;
3169 }
3170 } else {
3171 /*---Subsonic Case: Psi-rho E term from volume, objective-specific terms which are common
3172 * between subsonic and supersonic cases are added later ---*/
3173 /*--- Compute Riemann constant ---*/
3174 Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
3175 Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
3176
3177 /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
3178 Density = pow(P_Exit/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
3179 SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*P_Exit/Density);
3180 Vn_Exit = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
3181 /*--- Update velocity terms ---*/
3182 Vn_rel = Vn_Exit-ProjGridVel;
3183
3184 Velocity2 = 0.0;
3185 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3186 Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Exit-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
3187 Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
3188 }
3189
3190 /*--- Extra boundary term for grid movement ---*/
3191
3192 if (grid_movement) {
3193 ProjGridVel = 0.0;
3194 su2double *GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
3195 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3196 ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
3197 }
3198
3199 /*--- Impose values for PsiRho & Phi using PsiE from domain. ---*/
3200
3201 Psi_outlet[nVar-1] = Psi_domain[nVar-1];
3202
3203 }
3204
3205 /*--- When Psi_outlet[nVar-1] is not 0, the other terms of Psi_outlet must be updated
3206 This occurs when subsonic, or for certain objective functions ---*/
3207 if ( Psi_outlet[nVar-1] !=0.0 ) {
3208 /*--- Shorthand for repeated term in the boundary conditions ---*/
3209 a1 = 0.0;
3210 if (Vn!=0.0)
3211 a1 = SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One/Vn;
3212 Psi_outlet[0] += Psi_outlet[nVar-1]*(Velocity2*0.5+Vn_rel*a1);
3213 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3214 Psi_outlet[iDim+1] += -Psi_outlet[nVar-1]*(a1*UnitNormal[iDim] + Velocity[iDim]);
3215 }
3216 }
3217
3218
3219 /*--- Add terms for objective functions where additions are needed outside the energy term
3220 * Terms which are added to the energy term are taken care of in the supersonic section above ---*/
3221 switch (config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring)) {
3222 case SURFACE_MASSFLOW:
3223 Psi_outlet[0]+=Weight_ObjFunc;
3224 break;
3225 case SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE:
3226 /*--- For total pressure objective function. NOTE: this is AREA averaged term---*/
3227 Velocity2 = 0.0;
3228 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3229 Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
3230 if (Vn_Exit !=0.0) {
3231 a2 = Pressure*(Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One)*pow((1.0+Gamma_Minus_One*Density*Velocity2/(2.0*Gamma*Pressure)),1.0/(Gamma_Minus_One));
3232 density_gradient = a2*(Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2/(2.0*Gamma*Pressure));
3233 velocity_gradient=a2*Gamma_Minus_One*Density/(Gamma*Pressure); // re-using variable as the constant multiplying V[i] for dj/dvi
3234 Psi_outlet[0]+=Weight_ObjFunc*(density_gradient*2.0/Vn_Exit);
3235 for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++) {
3236 Psi_outlet[0]-=Weight_ObjFunc*(velocity_gradient*Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]/(Density*Vn_Exit));
3237 Psi_outlet[iDim+1] += Weight_ObjFunc*(velocity_gradient*Velocity[iDim]/(Density*Vn_Exit) - UnitNormal[iDim]*density_gradient/(Vn_Exit*Vn_Exit));
3238 }
3239 }
3240 break;
3241 case SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE:
3242 /*0.0*/
3243 break;
3244 default:
3245 break;
3246 }
3247
3248 /*--- Set the flow and adjoint states in the solver ---*/
3249
3250 conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
3251 conv_numerics->SetAdjointVar(Psi_domain, Psi_outlet);
3252
3253 /*--- Grid Movement ---*/
3254
3255 if (grid_movement)
3256 conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
3257 geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
3258
3259 conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij,
3260 Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
3261
3262 /*--- Add and Subtract Residual ---*/
3263
3264 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
3265
3266 /*--- Implicit contribution to the residual ---*/
3267
3268 if (implicit)
3269 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
3270
3271 /*--- Viscous residual contribution, it doesn't work ---*/
3272
3273 if (config->GetViscous()) {
3274
3275 /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
3276 V_outlet[nDim+5] = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
3277 V_outlet[nDim+6] = solver_container[FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
3278
3279 /*--- Points in edge, coordinates and normal vector---*/
3280 visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
3281 su2double Coord_Reflected[3];
3282 GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
3283 geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
3284 visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
3285
3286 /*--- Conservative variables w/o reconstruction and adjoint variables w/o reconstruction---*/
3287
3288 visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
3289 visc_numerics->SetAdjointVar(Psi_domain, Psi_outlet);
3290
3291 /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
3292
3293 if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
3294 visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0), solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
3295
3296 /*--- Gradient and limiter of Adjoint Variables ---*/
3297
3298 visc_numerics->SetAdjointVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient(iPoint));
3299
3300 /*--- Compute residual ---*/
3301
3302 visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual_i, Residual_j, Jacobian_ii, Jacobian_ij, Jacobian_ji, Jacobian_jj, config);
3303
3304 /*--- Update adjoint viscous residual ---*/
3305
3306 LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual_i);
3307
3308 if (implicit)
3309 Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_ii);
3310
3311 }
3312 }
3313 }
3314
3315 /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
3316
3317 delete [] Normal;
3318 delete [] Psi_domain; delete [] Psi_outlet;
3319
3320}

3762 /*--- Volume at time n-1 and n ---*/
3763 if (Grid_Movement) {
3764 Volume_nM1 = geometry->nodes->GetVolume_nM1(iPoint);
3765 Volume_n = geometry->nodes->GetVolume_n(iPoint);
3766 Volume_nP1 = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
3767 }
3768 else {
3769 Volume_nM1 = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
3770 Volume_n = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
3771 Volume_nP1 = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
3772 }
3773
3774 /*--- Time Step ---*/
3775 TimeStep = config->GetDelta_UnstTimeND();
3776
3777 /*--- Compute Residual ---*/
3778 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
3779 if (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST)
3780 Residual[iVar] = ( U_time_nP1[iVar]*Volume_nP1 - U_time_n[iVar]*Volume_n ) / TimeStep;
3781 if (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND)
3782 Residual[iVar] = ( 3.0*U_time_nP1[iVar]*Volume_nP1 - 4.0*U_time_n[iVar]*Volume_n
3783 + 1.0*U_time_nM1[iVar]*Volume_nM1 ) / (2.0*TimeStep);
3784 }
3785
3786 /*--- Add Residual ---*/
3787 LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
3788
3789 if (implicit) {
3790 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
3791 for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
3792 Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
3793
3794 if (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST)
3795 Jacobian_i[iVar][iVar] = Volume_nP1 / TimeStep;
3796 if (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND)
3797 Jacobian_i[iVar][iVar] = (Volume_nP1*3.0)/(2.0*TimeStep);
3798 }
3799 Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_i);
3800 }
3801 }
3802
3803}

3805void CAdjEulerSolver::LoadRestart(CGeometry **geometry, CSolver ***solver, CConfig *config, int val_iter, bool val_update_geo) {
3806
3807 /*--- Restart the solution from file information ---*/
3808 unsigned short iDim, iVar, iMesh;
3809 unsigned long index;
3810 su2double *Coord;
3811 string filename, restart_filename;
3812
3813 /*--- Restart the solution from file information ---*/
3814
3815 filename = config->GetSolution_AdjFileName();
3816 restart_filename = config->GetObjFunc_Extension(filename);
3817 restart_filename = config->GetFilename(restart_filename, "", val_iter);
3818
3819 Coord = new su2double [nDim];
3820 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3821 Coord[iDim] = 0.0;
3822
3823 /*--- Skip coordinates ---*/
3824
3825 unsigned short skipVars = geometry[MESH_0]->GetnDim();
3826
3827 /*--- Read the restart data from either an ASCII or binary SU2 file. ---*/
3828
3829 if (config->GetRead_Binary_Restart()) {
3830 Read_SU2_Restart_Binary(geometry[MESH_0], config, restart_filename);
3831 } else {
3832 Read_SU2_Restart_ASCII(geometry[MESH_0], config, restart_filename);
3833 }
3834
3835 /*--- Load data from the restart into correct containers. ---*/
3836
3837 int counter = 0;
3838 long iPoint_Local = 0; unsigned long iPoint_Global = 0;
3839 unsigned long iPoint_Global_Local = 0;
3840 unsigned short rbuf_NotMatching = 0, sbuf_NotMatching = 0;
3841
3842 for (iPoint_Global = 0; iPoint_Global < geometry[MESH_0]->GetGlobal_nPointDomain(); iPoint_Global++ ) {
3843
3844 /*--- Retrieve local index. If this node from the restart file lives
3845 on the current processor, we will load and instantiate the vars. ---*/
3846
3847 iPoint_Local = geometry[MESH_0]->GetGlobal_to_Local_Point(iPoint_Global);
3848
3849 if (iPoint_Local > -1) {
3850
3851 /*--- We need to store this point's data, so jump to the correct
3852 offset in the buffer of data from the restart file and load it. ---*/
3853
3854 index = counter*Restart_Vars[1] + skipVars;
3855 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Solution[iVar] = Restart_Data[index+iVar];
3856
3857 nodes->SetSolution(iPoint_Local,Solution);
3858 iPoint_Global_Local++;
3859
3860 /*--- Increment the overall counter for how many points have been loaded. ---*/
3861 counter++;
3862 }
3863 }
3864
3865 /*--- Detect a wrong solution file ---*/
3866
3867 if (iPoint_Global_Local < nPointDomain) { sbuf_NotMatching = 1; }
3868
3869#ifndef HAVE_MPI
3870 rbuf_NotMatching = sbuf_NotMatching;
3871#else
3872 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&sbuf_NotMatching, &rbuf_NotMatching, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
3873#endif
3874 if (rbuf_NotMatching != 0) {
3875 SU2_MPI::Error(string("The solution file ") + filename + string(" doesn't match with the mesh file!\n") +
3876 string("It could be empty lines at the end of the file."), CURRENT_FUNCTION);
3877 }
3878
3879 /*--- Communicate the loaded solution on the fine grid before we transfer
3880 it down to the coarse levels. We also call the preprocessing routine
3881 on the fine level in order to have all necessary quantities updated. ---*/
3882
3883 solver[MESH_0][ADJFLOW_SOL]->InitiateComms(geometry[MESH_0], config, SOLUTION);
3884 solver[MESH_0][ADJFLOW_SOL]->CompleteComms(geometry[MESH_0], config, SOLUTION);
3885 solver[MESH_0][ADJFLOW_SOL]->Preprocessing(geometry[MESH_0], solver[MESH_0], config, MESH_0, NO_RK_ITER, RUNTIME_FLOW_SYS, false);
3886
3887 /*--- Interpolate the solution down to the coarse multigrid levels ---*/
3888
3889 for (iMesh = 1; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
3890 MultigridRestriction(*geometry[iMesh - 1], solver[iMesh - 1][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(),
3891 *geometry[iMesh], solver[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution());
3892 solver[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->InitiateComms(geometry[iMesh], config, SOLUTION);
3893 solver[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->CompleteComms(geometry[iMesh], config, SOLUTION);
3894 solver[iMesh][ADJFLOW_SOL]->Preprocessing(geometry[iMesh], solver[iMesh], config, iMesh, NO_RK_ITER, RUNTIME_FLOW_SYS, false);
3895 }
3896
3897 delete [] Coord;
3898
3899 /*--- Delete the class memory that is used to load the restart. ---*/
3900
3901 Restart_Vars = decltype(Restart_Vars){};
3902 Restart_Data = decltype(Restart_Data){};
3903}

3905void CAdjEulerSolver::SetAuxVar_Surface_Gradient(CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig *config) {
3906
3907 unsigned short iDim, jDim, iNeigh, iMarker;
3908 unsigned short nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
3909 unsigned long iPoint, jPoint, iVertex;
3910 su2double *Coord_i, *Coord_j, AuxVar_i, AuxVar_j;
3911 su2double **Smatrix, *Cvector;
3912
3913 Smatrix = new su2double* [nDim];
3914 Cvector = new su2double [nDim];
3915 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3916 Smatrix[iDim] = new su2double [nDim];
3917
3918
3919 /*--- Loop over boundary markers to select those for Euler or NS walls ---*/
3920 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3921
3922 if (config->GetSolid_Wall(iMarker)) {
3923
3924 /*--- Loop over points on the surface (Least-Squares approximation) ---*/
3925 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
3926 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3927 if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
3928 Coord_i = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
3929 AuxVar_i = nodes->GetAuxVar(iPoint);
3930
3931 /*--- Inizialization of variables ---*/
3932 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3933 Cvector[iDim] = 0.0;
3934 su2double r11 = 0.0, r12 = 0.0, r13 = 0.0, r22 = 0.0, r23 = 0.0, r23_a = 0.0, r23_b = 0.0, r33 = 0.0;
3935
3936 for (iNeigh = 0; iNeigh < geometry->nodes->GetnPoint(iPoint); iNeigh++) {
3937 jPoint = geometry->nodes->GetPoint(iPoint, iNeigh);
3938 Coord_j = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(jPoint);
3939 AuxVar_j = nodes->GetAuxVar(jPoint);
3940
3941 su2double weight = 0;
3942 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3943 weight += (Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim])*(Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim]);
3944
3945 /*--- Sumations for entries of upper triangular matrix R ---*/
3946 r11 += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])/weight;
3947 r12 += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])/weight;
3948 r22 += (Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])*(Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])/weight;
3949 if (nDim == 3) {
3950 r13 += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
3951 r23_a += (Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
3952 r23_b += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
3953 r33 += (Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
3954 }
3955
3956 /*--- Entries of c:= transpose(A)*b ---*/
3957 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3958 Cvector[iDim] += (Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim])*(AuxVar_j-AuxVar_i)/weight;
3959 }
3960
3961 /*--- Entries of upper triangular matrix R ---*/
3962 r11 = sqrt(r11);
3963 r12 = r12/r11;
3964 r22 = sqrt(r22-r12*r12);
3965 if (nDim == 3) {
3966 r13 = r13/r11;
3967 r23 = r23_a/r22 - r23_b*r12/(r11*r22);
3968 r33 = sqrt(r33-r23*r23-r13*r13);
3969 }
3970 /*--- S matrix := inv(R)*traspose(inv(R)) ---*/
3971 if (nDim == 2) {
3972 su2double detR2 = (r11*r22)*(r11*r22);
3973 Smatrix[0][0] = (r12*r12+r22*r22)/detR2;
3974 Smatrix[0][1] = -r11*r12/detR2;
3975 Smatrix[1][0] = Smatrix[0][1];
3976 Smatrix[1][1] = r11*r11/detR2;
3977 }
3978 else {
3979 su2double detR2 = (r11*r22*r33)*(r11*r22*r33);
3980 su2double z11, z12, z13, z22, z23, z33; // aux vars
3981 z11 = r22*r33;
3982 z12 = -r12*r33;
3983 z13 = r12*r23-r13*r22;
3984 z22 = r11*r33;
3985 z23 = -r11*r23;
3986 z33 = r11*r22;
3987 Smatrix[0][0] = (z11*z11+z12*z12+z13*z13)/detR2;
3988 Smatrix[0][1] = (z12*z22+z13*z23)/detR2;
3989 Smatrix[0][2] = (z13*z33)/detR2;
3990 Smatrix[1][0] = Smatrix[0][1];
3991 Smatrix[1][1] = (z22*z22+z23*z23)/detR2;
3992 Smatrix[1][2] = (z23*z33)/detR2;
3993 Smatrix[2][0] = Smatrix[0][2];
3994 Smatrix[2][1] = Smatrix[1][2];
3995 Smatrix[2][2] = (z33*z33)/detR2;
3996 }
3997 /*--- Computation of the gradient: S*c ---*/
3998 su2double product;
3999 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4000 product = 0.0;
4001 for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim++)
4002 product += Smatrix[iDim][jDim]*Cvector[jDim];
4003 nodes->SetAuxVarGradient(iPoint, 0, iDim, product);
4004 }
4005 }
4006 } /*--- End of loop over surface points ---*/
4007 }
4008 }
4009
4010 /*--- Memory deallocation ---*/
4011 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4012 delete [] Smatrix[iDim];
4013 delete [] Cvector;
4014 delete [] Smatrix;
4015}
